Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,2,,片名：梦幻成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,2,,先父名叫约翰康斯拉\NMy father's name was John Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,2,,这是个爱尔兰名字\NIt's an Irish name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,2,,他于1896年出生在北达科他州\NHe was born in North Dakota in 1896
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,2,,在1918年从法国回来以前 从没见过大城市\Nand never saw a big city until he came back from France in 1918.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.52,Default,,0,0,2,,后来他定居芝加哥\NSettling in Chicago, he learned to live and die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,2,,没多久就让白袜职棒队 控制了他的喜怒哀乐\Nwith the White Sox.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,2,,当他们输了1919年的 世界大赛时，他有些不悦\NDied a little when they lost the 1919 World Series,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.56,Default,,0,0,2,,“我们是诈输的” 但是到了夏天\Ndied a lot when eight White Sox were accused of throwing that Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:01.26,Default,,0,0,2,,“两名白袜队球员坦承” 当八名球员\N“我们是诈输的” 但是到了夏天\Ndied a lot when eight White Sox were accused of throwing that Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,2,,“我们是诈输的” 但是到了夏天\Ndied a lot when eight White Sox were accused of throwing that Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,2,,被指控故意输球时 他的心碎了\NHe played some in the minors, but nothing came of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,2,,他在小联盟打了一、两年的棒球 可惜没多大发展\N被指控故意输球时 他的心碎了\NHe played some in the minors, but nothing came of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:06.21,Default,,0,0,2,,他在小联盟打了一、两年的棒球 可惜没多大发展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,2,,在三十五岁时搬到布鲁克林\NMoved to Brooklyn in '35, married Mom in '38,\N他在小联盟打了一、两年的棒球 可惜没多大发展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:10.54,Default,,0,0,2,,在三十五岁时搬到布鲁克林\NMoved to Brooklyn in '35, married Mom in '38,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,2,,三十八岁和母亲结婚\Nwas already an old man at the naval yards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,2,,我在1952年出生\Nwhen I was born in 1952.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,2,,那时他已经是个 在海军工场工作的老人\N我在1952年出生\Nwhen I was born in 1952.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,2,,那时他已经是个 在海军工场工作的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:16.85,Default,,0,0,2,,我的名字是瑞康斯拉\NMy name's Ray Kinsella.\N那时他已经是个 在海军工场工作的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.47,Default,,0,0,2,,我的名字是瑞康斯拉\NMy name's Ray Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,2,,三岁时母亲过逝，而我…\NMom died when I was three, and I suppose Dad did the best he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,2,,我想父亲 的确尽了他最大的努力\NInstead of Mother Goose, I was put to bed to stories of Babe Ruth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,2,,每晚的睡前故事不是鹅妈妈\N我想父亲 的确尽了他最大的努力\NInstead of Mother Goose, I was put to bed to stories of Babe Ruth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我想父亲 的确尽了他最大的努力\NInstead of Mother Goose, I was put to bed to stories of Babe Ruth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,2,,“名棒球选手” 而是贝比鲁斯、贾里格\NLou Gehrig, and the great Shoeless Joe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:30.86,Default,,0,0,2,,以及伟大的“赤脚乔”杰克森\N“名棒球选手” 而是贝比鲁斯、贾里格\NLou Gehrig, and the great Shoeless Joe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,2,,以及伟大的“赤脚乔”杰克森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.20,Default,,0,0,2,,Dad was a Yankees fan then, so I rooted for Brooklyn.\N以及伟大的“赤脚乔”杰克森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,2,,Dad was a Yankees fan then, so I rooted for Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,2,,父亲是纽约洋基队的球迷 而我则替布鲁克林道奇队加油\NDad was a Yankees fan then, so I rooted for Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,2,,父亲是纽约洋基队的球迷 而我则替布鲁克林道奇队加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,2,,但是在1958年道奇队搬走了\NIn '58, the Dodgers moved away, so we had to find other reasons to fight.\N父亲是纽约洋基队的球迷 而我则替布鲁克林道奇队加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,2,,但是在1958年道奇队搬走了\NIn '58, the Dodgers moved away, so we had to find other reasons to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,2,,我们又得找别的话题来争执\N但是在1958年道奇队搬走了\NIn '58, the Dodgers moved away, so we had to find other reasons to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,2,,我们又得找别的话题来争执
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,2,,也的确找到了\NWe did.\N我们又得找别的话题来争执
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:41.78,Default,,0,0,2,,也的确找到了\NWe did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.74,Default,,0,0,2,,到了选大学的时候\NWhen I chose a college,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,2,,我选了离家最远的学校\NI picked the farthest from home I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,2,,“柏克莱大学” 这当然让他火冒三丈\NThis drove him up the wall, which, I suppose, was the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.17,Default,,0,0,2,,其实是我故意这么做的\N“柏克莱大学” 这当然让他火冒三丈\NThis drove him up the wall, which, I suppose, was the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,2,,其实是我故意这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,2,,当时我主修英文\NOfficially, my major was English, but really, it was the '60s.\N其实是我故意这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,2,,当时我主修英文\NOfficially, my major was English, but really, it was the '60s.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,2,,但是别忘了，那是六零年代\NI marched, I smoked some grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,2,,“做爱不作战” 我示威游行过，也抽过大麻\NI tried to like sitar music, and I met Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:03.22,Default,,0,0,2,,更试着接受西塔琴音乐 后来遇到了安妮\N“做爱不作战” 我示威游行过，也抽过大麻\NI tried to like sitar music, and I met Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,2,,更试着接受西塔琴音乐 后来遇到了安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,2,,我们唯一的共同点是 她来自爱荷华\NThe only thing we had in common\N更试着接受西塔琴音乐 后来遇到了安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,2,,我们唯一的共同点是 她来自爱荷华\NThe only thing we had in common
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,2,,was that she came from Iowa, and I'd once heard of Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,2,,而我曾经听过爱荷华\Nwas that she came from Iowa, and I'd once heard of Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,2,,而我曾经听过爱荷华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,2,,毕业后，我们搬到中西部去\NAfter graduation, we moved to the Midwest\N而我曾经听过爱荷华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,2,,毕业后，我们搬到中西部去\NAfter graduation, we moved to the Midwest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,2,,至于和她家人 相处的最大极限是…\Nand stayed with her family as long as we could,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,2,,一个下午\Nalmost a full afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,2,,我们在1974年的六月结婚\NAnnie and I got married in June of '74.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,2,,父亲就在那年的秋天去世\NDad died that fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.04,Default,,0,0,2,,几年后，凯伦诞生了\NA few years later, Karin was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,2,,虽然闻起来怪怪的 但我们仍然深爱着她\NShe smelled weird, but we loved her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,2,,后来安妮发了奇想 居然说服我买下一座农场\NThen Annie got the crazy idea she could talk me into buying a farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,2,,我现在三十六岁 热爱我的家人和棒球\NI'm 36 years old, I love my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,2,,I love baseball, and I'm about to become a farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,2,,“已出售” 而我即将成为一个农夫\NI love baseball, and I'm about to become a farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,2,,“已出售” 而我即将成为一个农夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,2,,但我必须澄清一点\NBut until I heard the voice,\N“已出售” 而我即将成为一个农夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,2,,但我必须澄清一点\NBut until I heard the voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,2,,在听到那个声音之前 我从没做过疯狂的事\NI'd never done a crazy thing in my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了，他就会来\NIf you build it, he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了，他就会来\NIf you build it, he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.75,Default,,0,0,2,,喂，安妮\NHey, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,2,,那是什么？ 你在说什么？\NAnnie, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,2,,What was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.64,Default,,0,0,2,,刚才的声音到底是什么意思？\NThat voice just now. What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,2,,我们没听到任何声音\NWe didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.77,Default,,0,0,2,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了，他就会来\NIf you build it, he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,2,,你现在总该听到了吧\NOkay, you must have heard that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,2,,还是没有，进来吃晚饭啦\NSorry. Hey, come on in to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.46,Default,,0,0,2,,Let's go, pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,2,,公路上是不是有扩音器？\NIs there, like, a sound truck on the highway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,2,,没有\NNope. Hey, Karin, dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.61,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦，来吃饭啦\N没有\NNope. Hey, Karin, dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦，来吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,2,,有没有小孩在听收音机？ 没有\NKids with a radio?\N凯伦，来吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,2,,有没有小孩在听收音机？ 没有\NKids with a radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,2,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,2,,你真的听到声音？\NHey, are you really hearing voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,2,,只听到一次\NJust one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.41,Default,,0,0,2,,说什么？\NWhat did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,2,,“如果你盖了，他就会来”\N"If you build it, he will come."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,2,,盖什么、谁会来呢？\NIf you build what, who will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,2,,他没说\NHe didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,2,,我最讨厌这样子 我也是\NI hate it when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,2,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了，他就会来\NIf you build it, he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.30,Default,,0,0,2,,盖什么？这到底是什么意思 瑞\NBuild what? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.46,Default,,0,0,2,,Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.81,Default,,0,0,2,,别担心，没事的\NIt's okay, honey. I... I'm just talking to the cornfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,2,,我只是在和玉米田讲话\N别担心，没事的\NIt's okay, honey. I... I'm just talking to the cornfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,2,,我只是在和玉米田讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,2,,好啦，当我在走路的时候\NAnyway, I was walking down along the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,2,,and I heard this voice saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,2,,听到一个声音说 “陶先生，晚安”\N"Good evening, Mr. Dowd."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,2,,我一转身…\NWell, I turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,2,,and here was this big, six-foot rabbit leaning up against the lamppost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,2,,就看见一只六尺高的兔子 依着街灯的柱子\Nand here was this big, six-foot rabbit leaning up against the lamppost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,2,,就看见一只六尺高的兔子 依着街灯的柱子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,2,,你为什么要关掉，很好玩的\NWhy did you do that? It was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,2,,相信我，一点也不好玩 那个人有病，而且病得不轻\NTrust me, Karin. It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,2,,The man is sick. Very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦，吃完了就去拿书包 我们得走了\NKarin, honey, get your book bag. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,2,,今天我带她上学好了\NHon, I'll take her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.59,Default,,0,0,2,,我得进城买点东西\NI've got errands to do in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,2,,太好了\NFar out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.73,Default,,0,0,2,,Hey. What if the voice calls while you're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,2,,如果那声音又出现 我该怎么办？\NHey. What if the voice calls while you're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.36,Default,,0,0,2,,如果那声音又出现 我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,2,,就记下来吧      拜拜\NTake a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,2,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.15,Default,,0,0,2,,再见      再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,2,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,2,,这些年中，你有没有…\NIn all those years, did you ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.91,Default,,0,0,2,,有人告诉我在田里工作时\NIt's just I've heard that sometimes farmers in the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,2,,有时会听到奇怪的声音\NThey hear things. You know, voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,2,,你听到声音了？ 不是，是别人这么说的\NYou hearing voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,2,,No. It's just I heard some farmers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,2,,我当然没听过\NI, of course, don't, so I was wondering if I was doing something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,2,,所以我在想 是不是我哪里做错了\N我当然没听过\NI, of course, don't, so I was wondering if I was doing something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,2,,所以我在想 是不是我哪里做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,2,,你有没有听到过声音？ 谁听到声音？\NDid you... Did you ever hear voices out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,2,,Who's hearing voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,2,,是瑞…在田里面\NRay is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,2,,Out in the fields. No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,2,,我没有\NI'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,2,,是噪音\NNoises. That darned tractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,2,,那些牵引机的声…\N是噪音\NNoises. That darned tractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,2,,那些牵引机的声…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,2,,我只要再买点油就行了\NI'm just going to get some 3-in-1 oil. That ought to do it.\N那些牵引机的声…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,2,,我只要再买点油就行了\NI'm just going to get some 3-in-1 oil. That ought to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.29,Default,,0,0,2,,It was nice... Nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.86,Default,,0,0,2,,和你们…谈话很愉快\NIt was nice... Nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,2,,和你们…谈话很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了，他就会来\NIf you build it, he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,2,,好了，够啦，你他妈…\NAll right, that's it! Who the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,2,,你是谁，到底想干嘛？ 真是活见鬼了\NWho are you? What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,2,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了，他就会来\NIf you build it, he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,2,,If you build it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了\NIf you build it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你盖了\NIf you build it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,2,,he will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,2,,他就会来\Nhe will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,2,,他就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,2,,你确定不是迷幻药产生的幻觉\NYou don't suppose this is like an acid flashback, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,2,,我从没吃过迷幻药\NI never took acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,2,,也许那是 预言你将来会吃迷幻药\NMaybe you will someday. It's like a flash-forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，我想不止如此 宝贝，再多吃点\NAnnie, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,2,,Honey, why don't you eat a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,2,,I... I think I know what "If you build it, he will come" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,2,,我大概已经知道“如果你盖了 他就会来”的意思了\NI... I think I know what "If you build it, he will come" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,2,,我大概已经知道“如果你盖了 他就会来”的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,2,,哦，我有种不好的预感\NWhy do I not think this is so good?\N我大概已经知道“如果你盖了 他就会来”的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.14,Default,,0,0,2,,哦，我有种不好的预感\NWhy do I not think this is so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,2,,它的意思是 如果我在田里盖个棒球场\NI think it means that if I build a baseball field out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,2,,那么赤脚乔杰克森就会来打球\NShoeless Joe Jackson will get to come back and play ball again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.74,Default,,0,0,2,,你在开玩笑\NYou're kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,2,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,2,,哇！      对呀\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,2,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,2,,你一定在开玩笑\NYou're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,2,,你一定在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,2,,我一直以为我的家人够另类\NBoy, I thought my family was crazy, but this is the craziest thing ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,2,,没想到你比他们还厉害\NI know. It's totally nuts. I mean, Shoeless Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.72,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道听起来像胡说八道 你要知道赤脚乔…\N没想到你比他们还厉害\NI know. It's totally nuts. I mean, Shoeless Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道听起来像胡说八道 你要知道赤脚乔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,2,,已是一堆枯骨了 他死于1951年\NHe's dead. Died in '51. He's dead.\N我知道听起来像胡说八道 你要知道赤脚乔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,2,,已是一堆枯骨了 他死于1951年\NHe's dead. Died in '51. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,2,,当初他被迫离开棒球队吗？ 没错\NThey suspended him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,2,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,2,,他并没有复活吧？ 就我所知没有\NHe's still dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,2,,As far as I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,2,,你知道 贝比鲁斯就是学他的挥棒动作\NDid you know Babe Ruth copied his swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,2,,就算知道也忘了\NIf I did, I've forgotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,2,,他的挥棒是那么的优雅和敏捷\NHe was supposed to be so graceful and agile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.08,Default,,0,0,2,,若能再看到他打棒球…\NI'd actually like to see him play again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,2,,能让他再打球，并替他洗雪…\Nto let him play, to right an old wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,2,,等一等\NWait. Wait a minute, Bosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,2,,你真要盖个棒球场？\NAre you actually thinking of doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,2,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我实在找不出理由去盖它 但是…\NI mean, I can't think of one good reason why I should, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,2,,我已经三十六岁，有妻、有女 还有房屋贷款\NI'm 36. I have a wife, a child, and a mortgage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,2,,但我深怕 会步上我父亲的后尘\Nand I'm scared to death I'm turning into my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,2,,这和你父亲又有什么关系\NWhat's your father got to do with all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,2,,我永远不能原谅他的老去\NI never forgave him for getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,2,,当他在我现在这个年纪\NBy the time he was as old as I am now, he was ancient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,2,,已经老得动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,2,,他一定也有过梦想\NI mean, he must have had dreams, but he never did anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.35,Default,,0,0,2,,可惜没法去实现\N他一定也有过梦想\NI mean, he must have had dreams, but he never did anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.93,Default,,0,0,2,,可惜没法去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,2,,我猜他也曾听到过声音\NFor all I know, he may have even heard voices, too,\N可惜没法去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,2,,我猜他也曾听到过声音\NFor all I know, he may have even heard voices, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,2,,but he sure didn't listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,2,,却从来没有驻足倾听过\Nbut he sure didn't listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,2,,却从来没有驻足倾听过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,2,,就我所知 他从没做过率性而为的事\NThe man never did one spontaneous thing in all the years I knew him.\N却从来没有驻足倾听过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,2,,就我所知 他从没做过率性而为的事\NThe man never did one spontaneous thing in all the years I knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,2,,我不愿和他一样\NAnnie, I'm afraid of that happening to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:10.99,Default,,0,0,2,,在心灵的深处我感觉得到 这将是最后的机会了\Nand something tells me this may be my last chance to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,2,,我要盖个棒球场\NI want to build that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,2,,你说我疯了吗？\NDo you think I'm crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,2,,是疯了\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,2,,可是我也觉得…\NBut I also think if you really feel you should do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你真有这种感觉\N可是我也觉得…\NBut I also think if you really feel you should do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你真有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,2,,那就应该全力以赴\Nthen you should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.91,Default,,0,0,2,,他在搞什么鬼？\NWhat the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,2,,铲除玉米田呀      为什么？\NHe's plowing under his corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,2,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,2,,泰柯布被称为 史上最伟大的外野手\NTy Cobb called him the greatest left fielder of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,2,,他是见球就封\NHe said his glove was the place where triples go to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,2,,他能击球吗？ “他能击球吗？”\N- Could he hit? - Could he hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,2,,他平均打击率是零点三五六 是史上第三高的\NLifetime average. 356, third highest in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么叫他赤脚乔？\NWhy'd they call him Shoeless Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.19,Default,,0,0,2,,因为在他刚出道的时候 买了一双钉鞋\NWhen he was still in the minors,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,2,,he bought a new pair of spikes and hurt his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,2,,可是穿久了脚会痛 所以在第六局的时候\NIn the sixth inning, he took them off and played in his socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:27.07,Default,,0,0,2,,他就把鞋脱下来 穿着袜子打完全场\N可是穿久了脚会痛 所以在第六局的时候\NIn the sixth inning, he took them off and played in his socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,2,,他就把鞋脱下来 穿着袜子打完全场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.29,Default,,0,0,2,,其他球员 就戏称他为“赤脚乔”\NThe players kidded him,\N他就把鞋脱下来 穿着袜子打完全场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,2,,其他球员 就戏称他为“赤脚乔”\NThe players kidded him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,2,,called him "Shoeless Joe," and the name stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,2,,后来这个外号就流行开来\NHe's going to lose his farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,2,,他一定保不住这个农场 真是个笨蛋\NDamned fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.14,Default,,0,0,2,,Then in 1919, his team, the Chicago White Sox,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,2,,后来在1919年他的球队 就是芝加哥的白袜队\NThen in 1919, his team, the Chicago White Sox,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,2,,后来在1919年他的球队 就是芝加哥的白袜队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,2,,在世界大赛中诈输\Nthey threw the World Series.\N后来在1919年他的球队 就是芝加哥的白袜队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,2,,在世界大赛中诈输\Nthey threw the World Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,2,,什么是“诈输”？ 就是有人付钱让他们故意输\NWhat's "threw"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,2,,It means they lost on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,2,,Gamblers paid them to. Except Shoeless Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,2,,可是并不包括赤脚乔\NHe did take their money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.43,Default,,0,0,2,,虽然他的确拿了钱\Nbut nobody ever proved he did one thing to lose those games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,2,,可是却找不出他有诈输的动作\N虽然他的确拿了钱\Nbut nobody ever proved he did one thing to lose those games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,2,,可是却找不出他有诈输的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,2,,假如他真是故意输球\NIf he threw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.07,Default,,0,0,2,,how do you explain he hit .375 for the Series and committed no errors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,2,,那怎么解释他那 完美无缺的零点三七五打击率\Nhow do you explain he hit .375 for the Series and committed no errors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,2,,那怎么解释他那 完美无缺的零点三七五打击率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.47,Default,,0,0,2,,我不能   他打了十二枝安打\NI can't.\N那怎么解释他那 完美无缺的零点三七五打击率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,2,,我不能   他打了十二枝安打\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:06.40,Default,,0,0,2,,Twelve hits including the Series' only home run,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.65,Default,,0,0,2,,其中还包括全垒打\Nand they said he's trying to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,2,,他们居然说他是故意输的？ 太莫名其妙了\NIt's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,2,,八名棒球员中包括赤脚乔在内\NThe commissioner of baseball suspended eight of the players,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,2,,全被棒球委员会判终生停职\Nincluding the great Shoeless Joe Jackson, for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,2,,什么是“终生停职”？\NWhat's "suspend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,2,,就是终生不能再打棒球\NIt means they never let him play the game again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,2,,据我父亲说\NMy father said he saw him years later
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,2,,后来他曾在卡州的烂球场中 见到赤脚乔以化名在打球\Nplaying under a made-up name in some 10th-rate league in Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:35.60,Default,,0,0,2,,当时他臃肿肥胖完全没有活力\NHe'd put on 50 pounds, and his spring was gone from his step
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,2,,但仍能击出安打\Nbut he could still hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,2,,我爸爸常说 赤脚乔的打击举世无双\NDad used to say nobody could hit like Shoeless Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,2,,你知道当你说到你父亲时\NI think that's the first time I've ever seen you smile
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.49,Default,,0,0,2,,这是第一次你脸上有了笑容\Nwhen you mentioned your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,2,,好了…\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.71,Default,,0,0,2,,我做了件完全不合逻辑的事\NI have just created something totally illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,2,,我就喜欢这点\NThat's what I like about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,2,,我是不是彻底的疯了？\NAm I completely nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,2,,并不完全\NNot completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:24.02,Default,,0,0,2,,那是座很好的棒球场\NIt's a good baseball field, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,2,,而且还挺漂亮的   嗯\NIt's kind of pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,2,,有迹象吗？\NAny sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,2,,马上就会有事发生了\NSomething's going to happen out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,2,,我能感觉得到\NI can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.08,Default,,0,0,2,,对一个有经验的左投手\NSo, for the veteran southpaw, his summer of woes continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,2,,他的不幸仍然持续着\NThat's four straight hits in the inning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.37,Default,,0,0,2,,那是这局的第四支安打\NDaddy, what's a "southpaw"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，什么是“左投手”？\N那是这局的第四支安打\NDaddy, what's a "southpaw"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，什么是“左投手”？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,2,,就是用左手投球的投手\NIt means a left-handed pitcher, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,2,,到底有多糟？\NSo how bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,2,,少了好几亩玉米田的收入\NWell, considering how much less acreage we have for corn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我估计…应该正好打平\NI say we'll probably
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,2,,almost break even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,2,,我们把所有的储蓄全投下去了\NWe used up all our savings on that field, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地      凯伦等一下\NDaddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.91,Default,,0,0,2,,Just a minute, Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,2,,那你看棒球场能留吗？\NSo what are you saying? We can't keep the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,2,,留下的话可能连农场也保不住\NMakes it real hard to keep the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.55,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地   跟你说等一下嘛！\NDaddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,2,,In a minute, Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,2,,有个人在我们的新草坪上\NThere's a man out there on your lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,2,,我去煮咖啡，你到外面去呀\NI'll put up some coffee. Why don't you go on outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,2,,对不起\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.35,Default,,0,0,2,,我会打些球给你\NI'll get some out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.34,Default,,0,0,2,,我叫…瑞康斯拉\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.81,Default,,0,0,2,,Ray Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,2,,我是乔杰克森\NJoe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:26.09,Default,,0,0,2,,能再打球的感觉一定很好\NI bet it's good to be playing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:35.60,Default,,0,0,2,,自从被棒球委员会踢出去后\NGetting thrown out of baseball
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:39.77,Default,,0,0,2,,我整个人都瘫痪了\Nwas like having part of me amputated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,2,,我似乎听得到\NI've heard that old men wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.46,Default,,0,0,2,,and scratch itchy legs that have been dust for over 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:47.61,Default,,0,0,2,,在五十年后 一个老人醒过来搔腿的声音\Nand scratch itchy legs that have been dust for over 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:49.36,Default,,0,0,2,,在五十年后 一个老人醒过来搔腿的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,2,,那就是我\NThat was me.\N在五十年后 一个老人醒过来搔腿的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:50.87,Default,,0,0,2,,那就是我\NThat was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,2,,一天晚上我醒过来\NI'd wake up at night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:58.58,Default,,0,0,2,,鼻子闻到了球场的芳香\Nwith the smell of the ballpark in my nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:00.88,Default,,0,0,2,,with the cool of the grass on my feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,2,,脚下踩着冰凉的草地\Nwith the cool of the grass on my feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:03.31,Default,,0,0,2,,脚下踩着冰凉的草地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.80,Default,,0,0,2,,那是一种惊喜\Nthe thrill of the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:16.31,Default,,0,0,2,,你能投球吗？\NCan you pitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:19.06,Default,,0,0,2,,可以\NYeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:21.98,Default,,0,0,2,,而且还不错\Nnot bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.62,Default,,0,0,2,,我们需要捕手吗？\NDon't we need a catcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,2,,如果投在本垒板附近就不要\NNot if you get it near the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,2,,对\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:24:00.10,Default,,0,0,2,,我正在投球给赤脚乔\NI'm pitching to Shoeless Joe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.24,0:24:10.53,Default,,0,0,2,,打得好\NNice hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:27.80,Default,,0,0,2,,试试我的曲球\NSee if you can hit my curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:39.31,Default,,0,0,2,,你还真能打曲球\NYou can hit the curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.22,0:24:42.23,Default,,0,0,2,,投到这里来\NPut one right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.44,0:24:44.60,Default,,0,0,2,,好\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.53,0:25:00.95,Default,,0,0,2,,对啦，你最擅长打低球\NRight, you're a low ball hitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.04,0:25:03.21,Default,,0,0,2,,天呀，我真喜欢这个运动\NMan, I did love this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:08.17,Default,,0,0,2,,就算拿吃饭钱来换，我也愿意\NI'd have played for food money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.21,0:25:10.63,Default,,0,0,2,,那种比赛时的…\NIt was the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:13.63,Default,,0,0,2,,喧闹声和草香，深深吸引着我\Nthe sounds, the smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.51,0:25:19.93,Default,,0,0,2,,你有没有 把手套紧贴着脸的经验？\NDid you ever hold a ball or a glove to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.14,0:25:22.27,Default,,0,0,2,,有\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.77,0:25:26.48,Default,,0,0,2,,我最喜欢坐火车 到不同城市去旅行\NI used to love traveling on the trains from town to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.23,0:25:29.57,Default,,0,0,2,,像旅馆里…\NThe hotels,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.94,0:25:34.49,Default,,0,0,2,,大厅中的铜痰盂 和房间里的黄铜床\Nbrass spittoons in the lobbies, brass beds in the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:40.70,Default,,0,0,2,,还有群众们…\NIt was the crowd,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:45.96,Default,,0,0,2,,看到好安打 就站起来欢呼的盛况\Nrising to their feet when the ball was hit deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:51.30,Default,,0,0,2,,说实话…\NShoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.59,0:25:55.43,Default,,0,0,2,,就算不付钱我也愿意打球\NI'd have played for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.02,0:26:04.56,Default,,0,0,2,,那是我的家人\NIt's my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.02,0:26:09.81,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么要装灯？\NWhat's with the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.90,0:26:12.48,Default,,0,0,2,,All the stadiums have them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.44,0:26:15.11,Default,,0,0,2,,现在所有的球场都装了\NEven Wrigley Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.19,0:26:17.20,Default,,0,0,2,,即使是最落伍的球场也有 这样不容易看到球\NIt's harder to see the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.28,0:26:20.83,Default,,0,0,2,,都是那些老板们认为 晚上来看球赛的人会比较多\NThe owners found that more people can attend night games.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.33,0:26:22.58,Default,,0,0,2,,真拿他们没办法\NOwners.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:40.55,Default,,0,0,2,,杰克森先生，这是我太太安妮 还有我女儿凯伦\NMr. Jackson, this is my wife Annie and my daughter Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.64,0:26:42.68,Default,,0,0,2,,女士们好\NMa'am. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.89,0:26:45.98,Default,,0,0,2,,你是鬼吗？\NAre you a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.06,0:26:47.23,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦\NKarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.23,0:26:49.44,Default,,0,0,2,,她在开玩笑 没关系，你说呢？\NShe's kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.52,0:26:50.73,Default,,0,0,2,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.94,0:26:54.03,Default,,0,0,2,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.11,0:26:55.78,Default,,0,0,2,,你看起来很真实\NYou look real to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.24,0:26:58.11,Default,,0,0,2,,那么我就是真的啰\NThen I guess I'm real.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.70,0:27:00.95,Default,,0,0,2,,请到里面坐坐\NWould you like to come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.20,0:27:04.37,Default,,0,0,2,,噢，谢谢，我不能进去\NThanks. I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.25,0:27:15.17,Default,,0,0,2,,我能再来吗？\NCan I come back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.05,0:27:19.26,Default,,0,0,2,,当然可以，这是为你盖的\NYeah. I built this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:25.85,Default,,0,0,2,,你知道还有其他的人\NThere are others, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:31.15,Default,,0,0,2,,我们一共有八个人 他们会很感激的\NThere were eight of us. It would really mean a lot to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.40,0:27:35.53,Default,,0,0,2,,没问题 任何时间都欢迎你们来\NYeah, anytime. They're all welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.66,0:27:48.87,Default,,0,0,2,,嘿，这是天堂吗？\NHey, is this heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.91,0:27:50.92,Default,,0,0,2,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.29,0:27:54.63,Default,,0,0,2,,是爱荷华州\NIt's Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:03.39,Default,,0,0,2,,他要去哪里？ 不知道\NWhere's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.47,0:28:04.68,Default,,0,0,2,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.44,0:28:19.44,Default,,0,0,2,,我们一定要保住棒球场\NWe're keeping this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.44,0:28:23.11,Default,,0,0,2,,就算拼命也要留住它\NYou bet your ass we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.78,0:28:26.16,Default,,0,0,2,,你会把农场给丢了 少来啦\NYou're going to lose your farm, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.24,0:28:28.66,Default,,0,0,2,,它这么大，怎么会丢呢\NHow can you lose something so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.74,0:28:32.29,Default,,0,0,2,,有一次他把房子放错地方 但是两天后又找到了\NHe misplaced the house once. Yeah, but it turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.79,0:28:35.17,Default,,0,0,2,,对不对？\NRay, come on. Ray? Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.25,0:28:36.29,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你别这样\NThis stupid baseball field's going to bankrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.29,0:28:38.30,Default,,0,0,2,,大家都看得出来 这个讨厌的棒球场会拖垮你\N瑞，你别这样\NThis stupid baseball field's going to bankrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:38.38,Default,,0,0,2,,大家都看得出来 这个讨厌的棒球场会拖垮你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.38,0:28:39.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我只想提醒你 如果拖欠贷款你就会失去一切\NIf you default on your loan, you're going to lose everything.\N大家都看得出来 这个讨厌的棒球场会拖垮你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.31,0:28:42.30,Default,,0,0,2,,我只想提醒你 如果拖欠贷款你就会失去一切\NIf you default on your loan, you're going to lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.38,0:28:45.47,Default,,0,0,2,,最好卖给我的合伙人 他会给你个好价钱，你就能…\NMy partners will give you a fair price.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.55,0:28:47.72,Default,,0,0,2,,马克，谢谢你，但是我不卖\NThanks, Mark. Thanks, Mark, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.81,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,2,,不卖      好吧\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.35,0:28:51.81,Default,,0,0,2,,那我问你，为什么要待在这里\NWhat are you holding onto this place for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.89,0:28:53.73,Default,,0,0,2,,你从没喜欢过爱荷华州\NYou never liked Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.81,0:28:55.23,Default,,0,0,2,,你胡说      少装了\NThat's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.31,0:28:58.48,Default,,0,0,2,,你根本不喜欢耕作 而且对农事一无所知\NYou don't know the first thing about farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.57,0:29:02.15,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道的不少   是吗？\NI know a lot about farming. More than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.24,0:29:03.22,Default,,0,0,2,,比你想像的要多\NWell, then how could you plow under your major crop?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.22,0:29:05.53,Default,,0,0,2,,那你怎么会铲除你的庄稼呢\N比你想像的要多\NWell, then how could you plow under your major crop?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:06.15,Default,,0,0,2,,那你怎么会铲除你的庄稼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.49,0:29:07.99,Default,,0,0,2,,什么是庄稼？\NWhat's a crop?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:12.96,Default,,0,0,2,,好啦，别吵了\NCome on. That is funny. What's a crop?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.79,0:29:15.23,Default,,0,0,2,,什么是庄稼？\NDaddy, the baseball game is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.23,0:29:16.08,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，球赛要开始了 失陪一下\N什么是庄稼？\NDaddy, the baseball game is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.08,0:29:16.75,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，球赛要开始了 失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.75,0:29:18.09,Default,,0,0,2,,Excuse us.\N爹地，球赛要开始了 失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.09,0:29:19.29,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，球赛要开始了 失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:21.51,Default,,0,0,2,,我们先走一步\NExcuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.30,0:29:28.26,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，我真不敢相信这家伙\NAnnie, I don't believe this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.35,0:29:32.02,Default,,0,0,2,,我想救他，他却跑去看电视\NI'm trying to bail him out, and he leaves to watch television.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.10,0:29:34.19,Default,,0,0,2,,他以前还蛮正常的嘛 是呀\NHe used to be normal. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.26,0:30:11.43,Default,,0,0,2,,Buck!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.98,0:30:15.35,Default,,0,0,2,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.98,0:30:21.82,Default,,0,0,2,,Hoy! Hoy! Hoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.94,0:30:24.74,Default,,0,0,2,,好，回本垒\NAll right! Home base!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.40,0:30:28.07,Default,,0,0,2,,注意乔，看着他的脚\NWatch Joe's feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.57,0:30:32.99,Default,,0,0,2,,当投手收到信号准备投球时\NA good left fielder knows what pitch is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:33.86,Default,,0,0,2,,好的左外野手就能从…\NHe can tell from the bat's angle which way the ball's heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.86,0:30:36.87,Default,,0,0,2,,球棒和球接触的角度 而测知球的方向\N好的左外野手就能从…\NHe can tell from the bat's angle which way the ball's heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.87,0:30:37.45,Default,,0,0,2,,球棒和球接触的角度 而测知球的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.36,0:30:39.92,Default,,0,0,2,,耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.92,0:30:40.06,Default,,0,0,2,,又在耍酷了 甘德，你少在嘴上逞能\NShow off!\N耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.06,0:30:41.17,Default,,0,0,2,,又在耍酷了 甘德，你少在嘴上逞能\NShow off!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.42,0:30:43.05,Default,,0,0,2,,Stick it in your ear, Gandil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.13,0:30:47.17,Default,,0,0,2,,对，在和底特律比赛的时候 你若能跑得那么快\NIf you'd have run like that against Detroit, I'd have won 20 games!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.17,0:30:48.09,Default,,0,0,2,,那一年我们至少能赢二十场\N对，在和底特律比赛的时候 你若能跑得那么快\NIf you'd have run like that against Detroit, I'd have won 20 games!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.09,0:30:48.76,Default,,0,0,2,,那一年我们至少能赢二十场
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.76,0:30:49.44,Default,,0,0,2,,天呀，那是六十八年前的老帐 拜托别提了\NFor Pete's sakes, Cicotte, that was 68 years ago.\N那一年我们至少能赢二十场
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:51.60,Default,,0,0,2,,天呀，那是六十八年前的老帐 拜托别提了\NFor Pete's sakes, Cicotte, that was 68 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.68,0:30:53.01,Default,,0,0,2,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.10,0:30:54.78,Default,,0,0,2,,Hey! You guys want to play ball or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.78,0:30:57.10,Default,,0,0,2,,喂，你们到底要不要玩球\NHey! You guys want to play ball or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:57.73,Default,,0,0,2,,喂，你们到底要不要玩球
