Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.53,0:31:15.70,Default,,0,0,2,,没关系，我不介意\NIt's okay. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.12,0:31:17.87,Default,,0,0,2,,All right, Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.96,0:31:19.75,Default,,0,0,2,,Hey, hey, hey!
