Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:50.78,Default,,0,0,2,,你们不是要看球赛吗？\NThought you two were watching some game.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.16,0:31:54.28,Default,,0,0,2,,恐怕他们只能练球了\NIt's not really a game. It's more like practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.79,0:32:02.33,Default,,0,0,2,,你看他们只有八个人 所以不能比赛\NThere's only eight of them. They can't play a real game.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.34,0:32:06.84,Default,,0,0,2,,八个什么？\NEight of what?
