Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:14.43,Default,,0,0,2,,谁呀？      就是他们嘛\NWho them? Them them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.01,0:32:16.76,Default,,0,0,2,,难道你看不到他们？ 凯伦，你在看什么？\NYou don't see them?
