Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.94,0:33:04.56,Default,,0,0,2,,他们居然看不到他们\NThey couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:08.07,Default,,0,0,2,,这实在很有趣\NThis is really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.90,0:33:13.86,Default,,0,0,2,,嘿，瑞，你看看\NHey, Ray, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.95,0:33:17.58,Default,,0,0,2,,我穿这件制服已经六十八年了 仍旧这么合身\NSixty-eight years since I wore this uniform, still fits me like a glove.
