Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.67,0:38:22.25,Default,,0,0,2,,出去就出去\NFine!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.34,0:38:23.88,Default,,0,0,2,,Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.38,0:38:27.01,Default,,0,0,2,,坐下来   我没事\NAll right, honey. I've got a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.09,0:38:31.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我有个好主意 来投票表决，如何？\NLet's take a vote. Who's for Eva Braun?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.39,0:38:32.10,Default,,0,0,2,,谁赞成希特勒之妻？\NWho wants to burn books?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.10,0:38:33.89,Default,,0,0,2,,谁愿意去烧书？\N谁赞成希特勒之妻？\NWho wants to burn books?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.89,0:38:33.97,Default,,0,0,2,,谁愿意去烧书？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.97,0:38:34.29,Default,,0,0,2,,谁想反对美国宪法？\NWho wants to spit on the Constitution of the United States of America? Anybody?\N谁愿意去烧书？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.29,0:38:38.51,Default,,0,0,2,,谁想反对美国宪法？\NWho wants to spit on the Constitution of the United States of America? Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.51,0:38:38.73,Default,,0,0,2,,有人吗？\N谁想反对美国宪法？\NWho wants to spit on the Constitution of the United States of America? Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.73,0:38:40.44,Default,,0,0,2,,有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.19,0:38:48.49,Default,,0,0,2,,好，谁赞成权力法案？\NAll right. Now, who's for the Bill of Rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.57,0:38:51.74,Default,,0,0,2,,谁认为自由是件好事？\NWho thinks freedom is a pretty darn good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.91,0:38:55.91,Default,,0,0,2,,来呀！同意的请举手\NCome on! Come on! Let's see those hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:02.21,Default,,0,0,2,,谁认为我们应该从\NWho thinks we have to stand up to the kind of censorship
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.29,0:39:04.92,Default,,0,0,2,,史达林的审查制度中走出来？\Nthey had under Stalin?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.06,0:39:22.08,Default,,0,0,2,,这才是真正的美国人\NAll right. There you go. America, I love you. I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.08,0:39:23.82,Default,,0,0,2,,我爱你们、为你们感到骄傲 干什么？\N这才是真正的美国人\NAll right. There you go. America, I love you. I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.82,0:39:23.90,Default,,0,0,2,,我爱你们、为你们感到骄傲 干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.90,0:39:25.05,Default,,0,0,2,,我们得走了 我们走了，真过瘾\NLet's go. We got to go.\N我爱你们、为你们感到骄傲 干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.05,0:39:25.86,Default,,0,0,2,,我们得走了 我们走了，真过瘾\NLet's go. We got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.94,0:39:27.53,Default,,0,0,2,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.36,0:39:30.57,Default,,0,0,2,,我想出来了\NI figured it out. I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.28,0:39:34.12,Default,,0,0,2,,你看我是不是很厉害？ 我终于想出来了\NWas that great, or what? I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.20,0:39:37.08,Default,,0,0,2,,就像又回到六零年代一样 我刚想出来的\NIt's just like the '60s again! I just figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.16,0:39:39.16,Default,,0,0,2,,“到外面去，你这只纳粹猪” 我知道去抚平谁的伤痛了\N"Step outside, you Nazi cow."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.25,0:39:41.17,Default,,0,0,2,,I know whose pain I'm supposed to ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.29,0:39:43.67,Default,,0,0,2,,什么？ 我知道该去抚平谁的伤痛\NWhat? I know whose pain I'm supposed to ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.75,0:39:46.92,Default,,0,0,2,,我才制止那些人在美国 散布法西斯思想，你却说…\NI just halted the spread of neofascism in America...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.01,0:39:49.09,Default,,0,0,2,,泰伦斯孟\NTerence Mann. What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.17,0:39:51.55,Default,,0,0,2,,他怎么了？      就是他的伤痛\NThat's whose pain. You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:55.06,Default,,0,0,2,,你怎么知道？ 说不上来，就是知道嘛\NI was right about building the field, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:56.77,Default,,0,0,2,,当初盖球场还不是盖对了？\NWell, what's his pain? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.89,0:39:58.73,Default,,0,0,2,,没错，他有什么伤痛 我不知道\NHow are you supposed to ease it? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.81,0:40:00.77,Default,,0,0,2,,那你要怎么去抚平呢？ 也不知道\NRay. Well, Ann...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.85,0:40:03.90,Default,,0,0,2,,他也是我最喜欢的作家\NLook, he's my favorite writer, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.98,0:40:07.44,Default,,0,0,2,,但是他和棒球有什么关系？\Nbut what's Terence Mann got to do with baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.01,0:40:17.14,Default,,0,0,2,,“当我们最需要 泰伦斯孟的时候他在哪里？”
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.99,0:40:28.58,Default,,0,0,2,,“纽约大学逮捕五名 静坐抗议者——泰伦斯孟被捕”
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.56,0:40:34.19,Default,,0,0,2,,“20个有关美国 现存最伟大作家的传闻”
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.76,0:40:36.97,Default,,0,0,2,,“普立兹奖”\NAnnie, it's incredible. By the early '70s,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.97,0:40:37.06,Default,,0,0,2,,在七零年代初
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.06,0:40:39.59,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，他真了不起\NMann decides people have become either too extremist\N在七零年代初
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.59,0:40:39.60,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，他真了不起\NMann decides people have become either too extremist
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.68,0:40:41.48,Default,,0,0,2,,他发觉人们对他的理论 不是太激进就是太冷淡\Nor too apathetic to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.56,0:40:44.56,Default,,0,0,2,,So he stops writing books,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.65,0:40:45.94,Default,,0,0,2,,所以他停止写作\Nhe starts writing poetry about whales,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.94,0:40:47.61,Default,,0,0,2,,而开始写些鲸鱼的诗词\N所以他停止写作\Nhe starts writing poetry about whales,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.61,0:40:47.69,Default,,0,0,2,,而开始写些鲸鱼的诗词
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.69,0:40:48.74,Default,,0,0,2,,后来他迷上了家用电脑\Nand then he starts fooling around with a computer.\N而开始写些鲸鱼的诗词
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.74,0:40:51.11,Default,,0,0,2,,后来他迷上了家用电脑\Nand then he starts fooling around with a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.19,0:40:52.86,Default,,0,0,2,,你猜他现在做什么？ 猜不出\NKnow what he does now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.95,0:40:55.37,Default,,0,0,2,,他为儿童互动的节目 写电脑软体\NHe writes software for interactive children's videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.45,0:40:59.08,Default,,0,0,2,,教孩子们如何平静的解决冲突\NThey teach kids how to resolve their conflicts peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.83,0:41:01.62,Default,,0,0,2,,天啊！他真聪明 可是这和棒球有什么关系？\NGod, what an amazing guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.71,0:41:03.54,Default,,0,0,2,,What's that got to do with baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.62,0:41:05.71,Default,,0,0,2,,1962年四月份的喷射杂志中\NIn the April 1962 issue of Jet Magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.79,0:41:07.34,Default,,0,0,2,,there's a story called "This Is Not A Kite."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.34,0:41:08.88,Default,,0,0,2,,有一篇他写的故事叫做 “这并不是导管”\Nthere's a story called "This Is Not A Kite."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.88,0:41:08.96,Default,,0,0,2,,有一篇他写的故事叫做 “这并不是导管”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.96,0:41:10.71,Default,,0,0,2,,It's not his best work,\N有一篇他写的故事叫做 “这并不是导管”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.71,0:41:10.80,Default,,0,0,2,,有一篇他写的故事叫做 “这并不是导管”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.80,0:41:10.90,Default,,0,0,2,,虽然不是他最好的作品\Nbut the story's hero\N有一篇他写的故事叫做 “这并不是导管”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.90,0:41:14.09,Default,,0,0,2,,虽然不是他最好的作品\Nbut the story's hero
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.18,0:41:16.51,Default,,0,0,2,,但在二十六年前 他创造的英雄却叫约翰康斯拉\Nis named John Kinsella, my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.76,0:41:19.47,Default,,0,0,2,,就是我父亲      哇！\NWhat do you mean, "Wow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.56,0:41:20.79,Default,,0,0,2,,你这个“哇”是什么意思\NBig wow! What's it got to do with baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.79,0:41:23.60,Default,,0,0,2,,那你要我怎么说呢？ 但这和棒球有什么关系？\N你这个“哇”是什么意思\NBig wow! What's it got to do with baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.60,0:41:23.69,Default,,0,0,2,,那你要我怎么说呢？ 但这和棒球有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.69,0:41:24.74,Default,,0,0,2,,你来开\NYou drive.\N那你要我怎么说呢？ 但这和棒球有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.74,0:41:25.02,Default,,0,0,2,,你来开\NYou drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:33.45,Default,,0,0,2,,最后一次采访他 是在1973年，你猜主题是什么\NOkay, the last interview he ever gave was in 1973.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:34.78,Default,,0,0,2,,Guess what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.86,0:41:36.41,Default,,0,0,2,,是某种运动团体吗？\NSome kind of team sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.49,0:41:39.58,Default,,0,0,2,,Mann was a baseball fanatic. Listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.66,0:41:40.91,Default,,0,0,2,,他居然是个棒球迷 你听这一段\N"My earliest recurring dream was to play at Ebbets Field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.91,0:41:43.37,Default,,0,0,2,,“从儿时起，我的梦想就是 参加布鲁克林的道奇队”\N他居然是个棒球迷 你听这一段\N"My earliest recurring dream was to play at Ebbets Field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.37,0:41:43.46,Default,,0,0,2,,“从儿时起，我的梦想就是 参加布鲁克林的道奇队”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.46,0:41:44.37,Default,,0,0,2,,“在艾柏特球场 和杰基罗宾逊一起打球”\N"with Jackie Robinson and the Brooklyn Dodgers.\N“从儿时起，我的梦想就是 参加布鲁克林的道奇队”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.37,0:41:45.83,Default,,0,0,2,,“在艾柏特球场 和杰基罗宾逊一起打球”\N"with Jackie Robinson and the Brooklyn Dodgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.92,0:41:48.50,Default,,0,0,2,,“当然，这个梦永远没有实现 后来道奇离开布鲁克林”\N"It never happened. The Dodgers left Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.59,0:41:51.22,Default,,0,0,2,,“艾柏特球场也被拆了”\N"Ebbets Field is gone, but I still dream that dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.22,0:41:53.05,Default,,0,0,2,,“但是即使到了现在 我仍然常做这个梦”\N“艾柏特球场也被拆了”\N"Ebbets Field is gone, but I still dream that dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.05,0:41:53.38,Default,,0,0,2,,“但是即使到了现在 我仍然常做这个梦”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.38,0:41:54.45,Default,,0,0,2,,好悲哀哟\NThat's sad.\N“但是即使到了现在 我仍然常做这个梦”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.45,0:41:54.76,Default,,0,0,2,,好悲哀哟\NThat's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.22,0:42:00.26,Default,,0,0,2,,他写过他那时代最好的书\NThe man wrote the best books of his generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.06,0:42:04.73,Default,,0,0,2,,更是民权和反战运动的拓荒者\NHe was a pioneer in the civil rights and the antiwar movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.81,0:42:06.85,Default,,0,0,2,,他曾是新闻周刊的封面人物 他了解各种人，做过各种事\NI mean, he made the cover of Newsweek.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.94,0:42:10.94,Default,,0,0,2,,He knew everybody. He did everything. He helped shape his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.02,0:42:13.24,Default,,0,0,2,,他帮忙塑造了他的时代 甚至和披头四合唱团在一起过\NThe guy hung out with the Beatles.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.32,0:42:16.32,Default,,0,0,2,,但是到头来，还是不够 因为他没打成棒球\NIt wasn't enough. What he missed was baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.41,0:42:17.99,Default,,0,0,2,,喔，我的天！      什么事？\NOh, my God! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.07,0:42:21.20,Default,,0,0,2,,他小时候 有个球棒叫“玫瑰花蕾”\N"As a small boy, he had a bat named Rosebud."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.28,0:42:23.37,Default,,0,0,2,,让我看      抱歉\NGive me that. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.45,0:42:26.96,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，自从1958年后 他就一直没到球场看过球赛\NThe guy hasn't been to a baseball game since 1958.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.67,0:42:31.42,Default,,0,0,2,,所以为了抚平他的伤痛 你要带他去看球赛？\NSo, in order to ease his pain, you're supposed to take him to a ballgame.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.50,0:42:32.59,Default,,0,0,2,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.96,0:42:36.72,Default,,0,0,2,,Ray, this is nuttier than building the baseball field.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.80,0:42:38.05,Default,,0,0,2,,这比盖球场还疯狂\NNo. No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:40.14,Default,,0,0,2,,不，我同意这很荒谬\NIt's pretty weird, but building the field was 5, 10% weirder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.14,0:42:42.10,Default,,0,0,2,,但盖球场却比这更怪异\N不，我同意这很荒谬\NIt's pretty weird, but building the field was 5, 10% weirder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.10,0:42:42.18,Default,,0,0,2,,但盖球场却比这更怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.18,0:42:43.26,Default,,0,0,2,,抱歉老兄 这次我恐怕要反对了\NI'm going to have to nip this one in the bud.\N但盖球场却比这更怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.26,0:42:44.89,Default,,0,0,2,,抱歉老兄 这次我恐怕要反对了\NI'm going to have to nip this one in the bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:48.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我们的财务现在正陷入困境\NWe're having moderate-to-heavy financial difficulties here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.40,0:42:51.73,Default,,0,0,2,,当我们在爱荷华宣布破产时 你怎么可以躲到波士顿去\NAnd you can't take off for Boston while we're going broke in Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.82,0:42:54.07,Default,,0,0,2,,对我们来说这是个全新的领域\NThis is really new territory for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.15,0:42:56.74,Default,,0,0,2,,但是我们所接触的 是自然界的神奇力量\Nbut we're dealing with primal forces of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.82,0:43:00.87,Default,,0,0,2,,当这种力量叫你做事的时候\NThe prudent thing is not to quibble over details.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.95,0:43:02.39,Default,,0,0,2,,通常只讲大纲不讲细节\NYeah, but why do you have to go? Why can't the voice send somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.39,0:43:05.41,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么要你去做？ 为什么不叫别人去做？\N通常只讲大纲不讲细节\NYeah, but why do you have to go? Why can't the voice send somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.41,0:43:05.50,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么要你去做？ 为什么不叫别人去做？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.50,0:43:06.69,Default,,0,0,2,,叫莎利麦克莲去嘛，她又不忙\NHow about Shirley MacLaine? Is she too busy?\N为什么要你去做？ 为什么不叫别人去做？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.69,0:43:08.50,Default,,0,0,2,,叫莎利麦克莲去嘛，她又不忙\NHow about Shirley MacLaine? Is she too busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.58,0:43:10.58,Default,,0,0,2,,这和你有什么关系？ 所以我要去查明呀\NWhat does this have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.67,0:43:12.88,Default,,0,0,2,,That's what I have to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.96,0:43:17.09,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，我们的贷款快付不出来了\NRay, we are behind on the mortgage. That field ate up all of our savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.17,0:43:18.63,Default,,0,0,2,,球场把我们的积蓄全吃光 现在连农场怕也保不住\NWe could lose this farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.72,0:43:22.35,Default,,0,0,2,,我不住旅馆 就睡在车上，沿路向人乞食\NI won't even stay in motels. I'll sleep in the car. I'll beg for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.43,0:43:24.59,Default,,0,0,2,,No. No! Now, this is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.59,0:43:24.68,Default,,0,0,2,,这实在太过份了\NNo. No! Now, this is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.68,0:43:26.52,Default,,0,0,2,,这实在太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.10,0:43:31.15,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道你想向世界和自己证明\NNow, look. I understand your need to prove to yourself and to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.23,0:43:33.65,Default,,0,0,2,,你不会步上你父亲的后尘 可以你已经证明了\Nyou are not turning into your father, but you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.73,0:43:37.07,Default,,0,0,2,,你相信奇迹，它也发生了 难道这还不够吗？\NYou believed in the magic. It happened. Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.15,0:43:40.70,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，不止如此而已 我知道我像个疯子，可是…\NIt's more than that. I know this is totally nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.78,0:43:43.12,Default,,0,0,2,,but there's another reason I'm supposed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.20,0:43:44.74,Default,,0,0,2,,一定有要我去做的原因\NI feel it as strongly as I've felt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.74,0:43:46.45,Default,,0,0,2,,我从没有过这么强烈的感觉 一定有原因的\N一定有要我去做的原因\NI feel it as strongly as I've felt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.45,0:43:46.54,Default,,0,0,2,,我从没有过这么强烈的感觉 一定有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.54,0:43:47.54,Default,,0,0,2,,There's a reason.\N我从没有过这么强烈的感觉 一定有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.54,0:43:47.62,Default,,0,0,2,,我从没有过这么强烈的感觉 一定有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.62,0:43:48.34,Default,,0,0,2,,是什么？告诉我是什么原因\NWhat? Just tell me what it is.\N我从没有过这么强烈的感觉 一定有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.34,0:43:50.25,Default,,0,0,2,,是什么？告诉我是什么原因\NWhat? Just tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.33,0:43:52.08,Default,,0,0,2,,我觉得比赛时会有事发生 可是不知道…\NSomething's going to happen at the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.17,0:43:54.50,Default,,0,0,2,,There's something at Fenway Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.59,0:43:57.88,Default,,0,0,2,,但是我必须 和泰伦斯孟到芬威球场\NI got to be there with Terence Mann to find it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.97,0:44:00.20,Default,,0,0,2,,去找出原因来\NIs Fenway the one with the big green wall in left field?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.20,0:44:02.93,Default,,0,0,2,,芬威球场的左边 是不是有面大绿墙？\N去找出原因来\NIs Fenway the one with the big green wall in left field?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.93,0:44:03.55,Default,,0,0,2,,芬威球场的左边 是不是有面大绿墙？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.55,0:44:04.89,Default,,0,0,2,,是的\NYeah.\N芬威球场的左边 是不是有面大绿墙？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.89,0:44:05.06,Default,,0,0,2,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.52,0:44:10.10,Default,,0,0,2,,昨晚我梦到 你和泰伦斯孟在芬威球场\NI dreamt last night you were at Fenway with Terence Mann.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.94,0:44:13.61,Default,,0,0,2,,我是不是坐在一垒那边？ 对\NWas I sitting on the first base side? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.69,0:44:15.48,Default,,0,0,2,,差不多在一半的地方 没错，你在吃热狗\NAbout halfway up on the aisle?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.57,0:44:18.28,Default,,0,0,2,,Yeah. Eating a hot dog. Eating a hot dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.36,0:44:20.24,Default,,0,0,2,,我在吃热狗 我也做了同样的梦\NI had the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:21.49,Default,,0,0,2,,我去帮你装行李\NI'll help you pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.60,0:44:50.06,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，我是瑞康斯拉\NHi, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.14,0:44:51.98,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi, I'm Ray Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:53.69,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.77,0:44:55.06,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.15,0:44:58.53,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，我是瑞康斯拉 真高兴我们终于…\NHi, I'm Ray Kinsella. It's a great pleasure to finally get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.61,0:45:01.65,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，我是瑞康斯拉 非常崇拜你\NHi, I'm Ray Kinsella. I'm a big fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.74,0:45:02.78,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.11,0:45:05.24,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.07,0:45:08.12,Default,,0,0,2,,泰伦斯孟先生，你好 我要带你去看棒球赛\NHow do you do, Mr. Mann?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.20,0:45:10.54,Default,,0,0,2,,I have to take you to a base...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.58,0:45:14.79,Default,,0,0,2,,好吧，笨蛋，把手举起来 到行李箱里去\NAll right, stupid, put your hands up and get in the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.58,0:45:17.96,Default,,0,0,2,,这倒是好方法\NGood. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.46,0:45:21.97,Default,,0,0,2,,他就住在这附近 你认识他吗？\NHe lives right around here. Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.22,0:45:26.47,Default,,0,0,2,,他是个高个子的黑人 我是他的朋友\NHe's sort of a tall black man. I'm a friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.97,0:45:31.18,Default,,0,0,2,,既然是朋友 他就该告诉你怎么走\NIf he was much of a friend, he could give you the directions himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.14,0:45:36.65,Default,,0,0,2,,你说得不错，谢谢你\NThat's a good point. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.48,0:45:41.99,Default,,0,0,2,,走开，我不知道他住在哪里\NI don't know where he lives. Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.07,0:45:44.49,Default,,0,0,2,,我绝不会告诉你的 走开，讨厌鬼\NI ain't going to tell you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.57,0:45:46.99,Default,,0,0,2,,Go away! You're a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.24,0:45:53.37,Default,,0,0,2,,再过两条街的右手边\NTwo blocks down, right-hand side.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.46,0:45:57.00,Default,,0,0,2,,窗上没鸡的那扇门就是他的\NFirst door that don't have a chicken in the window is his.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.08,0:45:58.46,Default,,0,0,2,,没有鸡\NNo chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.73,0:46:06.67,Default,,0,0,2,,这里没鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.90,0:46:10.84,Default,,0,0,2,,“海达正统家禽、家畜店”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.82,0:46:23.88,Default,,0,0,2,,“联合电脑软体”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.71,0:46:45.51,Default,,0,0,2,,你是个什么东西？\NWho the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.84,0:46:51.30,Default,,0,0,2,,我的名字是瑞康斯拉\NSir, my name's Ray Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.57,0:47:12.12,Default,,0,0,2,,你的智商有问题吗？ 泰伦斯孟先生…\NWe got a learning disability here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:14.04,Default,,0,0,2,,If I could just have one minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.12,0:47:17.21,Default,,0,0,2,,请给我一分钟就好 你听着\NLook, I can't tell you the secret of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.29,0:47:19.25,Default,,0,0,2,,我不知道生命的秘密 也没有你要寻找的答案\Nand I don't have any answers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.92,0:47:23.34,Default,,0,0,2,,我不接受访问 也不再是公众人物\NI don't give interviews, and I'm no longer a public figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.42,0:47:26.26,Default,,0,0,2,,我只想安静的过日子 所以请你滚吧\NI just want to be left alone, so piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.22,0:47:29.01,Default,,0,0,2,,等一等\NWait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.93,0:47:32.10,Default,,0,0,2,,我开了1，500哩的路\NLook, I've come 1,500 miles to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.18,0:47:35.60,Default,,0,0,2,,冒着妻离家破的危险来看你\Nat the risk of losing my home and alienating my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.06,0:47:38.39,Default,,0,0,2,,我只要求你给我一分钟\NAll I'm asking is one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.48,0:47:40.65,Default,,0,0,2,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.52,0:47:45.90,Default,,0,0,2,,那就一分钟\NOne minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.20,0:47:58.12,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道你喜欢清净\NOkay, I understand your desire for privacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.12,0:48:02.42,Default,,0,0,2,,如果不是这么重要 我也不敢来打扰你\Nand I wouldn't dream of intruding if this weren't extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.50,0:48:06.38,Default,,0,0,2,,天呀，我已经不做诉讼了\NOh, God. I don't do causes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.76,0:48:08.51,Default,,0,0,2,,不是诉讼 也不是向你要钱或背书\NThis isn't a cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.59,0:48:10.76,Default,,0,0,2,,I don't need money or an endorsement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.84,0:48:12.39,Default,,0,0,2,,这倒挺新鲜的 你曾经写过…\NRefreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.64,0:48:13.80,Default,,0,0,2,,You once wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.89,0:48:17.85,Default,,0,0,2,,“当宇宙的齿轮 转到一个和谐点时”\N"There comes a time when all the cosmic tumblers have clicked into place
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.93,0:48:20.56,Default,,0,0,2,,“天地万物就会开放几秒钟”\N"and the universe opens itself up for a few seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.64,0:48:22.65,Default,,0,0,2,,"to show you what's possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.35,0:48:24.03,Default,,0,0,2,,“允许你看到未来”\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.03,0:48:24.77,Default,,0,0,2,,老天爷！      怎么啦？\N“允许你看到未来”\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.77,0:48:25.82,Default,,0,0,2,,老天爷！      怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.82,0:48:26.78,Default,,0,0,2,,What?\N老天爷！      怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.78,0:48:26.86,Default,,0,0,2,,老天爷！      怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.86,0:48:27.46,Default,,0,0,2,,你来自六零年代吧 对，实际上…\NYou're from the '60s.\N老天爷！      怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.46,0:48:28.44,Default,,0,0,2,,你来自六零年代吧 对，实际上…\NYou're from the '60s.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.53,0:48:30.49,Default,,0,0,2,,Well, yeah. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.15,0:48:32.41,Default,,0,0,2,,出去！再回到你的六零年代去 喂，等一下\NOut! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.49,0:48:34.07,Default,,0,0,2,,Back to the '60s.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.16,0:48:37.99,Default,,0,0,2,,在还能回去的时候快回去 这里根本不适合你\NNo place for you here in the future. Get back while you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.00,0:48:43.33,Default,,0,0,2,,你变了，你知道吧\NYou've changed, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.67,0:48:45.50,Default,,0,0,2,,我是变了，这样如何？\NYes, I suppose I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.59,0:48:47.86,Default,,0,0,2,,How about this? Peace, love, dope. Now get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.86,0:48:50.01,Default,,0,0,2,,和平、爱、毒品 你给我滚出去！\NHow about this? Peace, love, dope. Now get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.01,0:48:51.62,Default,,0,0,2,,和平、爱、毒品 你给我滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.72,0:49:36.93,Default,,0,0,2,,你现在真惹火我了 好，站在那里别动\NYou've really pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.01,0:49:38.51,Default,,0,0,2,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.14,0:49:40.97,Default,,0,0,2,,本来我不想这么做的\NI was hoping I wouldn't have to do it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.06,0:49:42.98,Default,,0,0,2,,那是什么鬼东西？ 枪，你以为是什么？\NWhat the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.06,0:49:44.60,Default,,0,0,2,,It's a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.69,0:49:45.85,Default,,0,0,2,,你的手指头      不，是枪\NIt's your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.94,0:49:47.31,Default,,0,0,2,,No, it's a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.40,0:49:48.77,Default,,0,0,2,,是吗？让我看 我才不会让你看我的枪\NLet me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.86,0:49:51.15,Default,,0,0,2,,I'm not going to show you my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.23,0:49:55.49,Default,,0,0,2,,放心，我不会伤害你 只是要你和我出去一下\NI'm not going to hurt you. I need you to come with...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.36,0:49:57.78,Default,,0,0,2,,你想干什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.87,0:50:00.49,Default,,0,0,2,,我会用铁撬打到你走为止\NI'll beat you with a crowbar until you go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.58,0:50:02.87,Default,,0,0,2,,你不能那么做 笑话，这还会有规矩吗？\NWait! You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.95,0:50:05.54,Default,,0,0,2,,There are rules here? No. There are no rules here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.54,0:50:06.00,Default,,0,0,2,,抱歉没有\NThere are rules here? No. There are no rules here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.00,0:50:07.25,Default,,0,0,2,,抱歉没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.25,0:50:08.63,Default,,0,0,2,,你本是个和平主义者\NYou're a pacifist!\N抱歉没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.63,0:50:08.92,Default,,0,0,2,,你本是个和平主义者\NYou're a pacifist!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.26,0:50:15.68,Default,,0,0,2,,该死\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.76,0:50:18.26,Default,,0,0,2,,谢谢你\NThank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.43,0:50:22.60,Default,,0,0,2,,你想绑架我吗？\NSo what? You kidnapping me? What's the deal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.73,0:50:25.14,Default,,0,0,2,,到底想干嘛？\NI was...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.15,0:50:29.98,Default,,0,0,2,,我只是想说服你和我一起出去\NI was hoping I could just convince you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.06,0:50:31.61,Default,,0,0,2,,所以就绑架我？\NSo you are kidnapping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.94,0:50:35.86,Default,,0,0,2,,我要带你去看棒球赛\NI have to take you to a baseball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.40,0:50:37.66,Default,,0,0,2,,你要干什么？ 去看今晚红袜对抗天使的比赛\NYou what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.20,0:50:40.78,Default,,0,0,2,,Tonight's game. Red Sox, A's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.87,0:50:41.95,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.83,0:50:45.16,Default,,0,0,2,,因为会有事发生 现在还不清楚\NSomething will happen there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.25,0:50:47.42,Default,,0,0,2,,I don't know what, but we'll find out when it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.42,0:50:48.54,Default,,0,0,2,,到时候我们自然会知道\NI don't know what, but we'll find out when it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.54,0:50:49.85,Default,,0,0,2,,到时候我们自然会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.29,0:50:52.55,Default,,0,0,2,,我叫瑞康斯拉 我父亲的名字是约翰康斯拉\NMy name's Ray Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.63,0:50:56.47,Default,,0,0,2,,You used my father's name for a character in one of your stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.55,0:50:58.09,Default,,0,0,2,,你曾在书中用过他的名字\NJohn Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.18,0:51:00.89,Default,,0,0,2,,你的精神病医生大概有一箩筐\NYou're seeing a whole team of psychiatrists, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.97,0:51:05.73,Default,,0,0,2,,我不怪你这么想 可是我真的没疯\NI don't blame you for thinking that, but, no, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.52,0:51:10.27,Default,,0,0,2,,我可以对天发誓 我真的很正常\NI swear to God, I'm the least crazy person I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.36,0:51:13.32,Default,,0,0,2,,那你为什么绑架我去看球赛\NWhy are you kidnapping me to a baseball game?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.65,0:51:15.86,Default,,0,0,2,,我可以坐… 请坐，要不要咖啡？\NMay I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.94,0:51:17.20,Default,,0,0,2,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.82,0:51:19.32,Default,,0,0,2,,Want a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.41,0:51:20.62,Default,,0,0,2,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.32,0:51:22.29,Default,,0,0,2,,不用了\NWant some cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.29,0:51:23.49,Default,,0,0,2,,饼干呢？\N不用了\NWant some cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.49,0:51:24.16,Default,,0,0,2,,不用了\NWant some cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.24,0:51:25.54,Default,,0,0,2,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.41,0:51:29.96,Default,,0,0,2,,也不要\NI read an interview you gave a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.04,0:51:32.50,Default,,0,0,2,,我看过一篇很久以前你的专访\Nabout how you always dreamed of playing at Ebbets Field
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.59,0:51:35.51,Default,,0,0,2,,其中提到你的梦想 是在艾柏特球场打球\Nand how sad you felt when they tore it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.59,0:51:36.65,Default,,0,0,2,,还有当他们拆除球场时 你有多伤心\NI never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.65,0:51:37.01,Default,,0,0,2,,我从没说过\N还有当他们拆除球场时 你有多伤心\NI never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.01,0:51:37.94,Default,,0,0,2,,我从没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.26,0:51:39.43,Default,,0,0,2,,你没有？ 我连想也没想过\NYou didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.51,0:51:41.34,Default,,0,0,2,,I don't even recall thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.39,0:51:47.18,Default,,0,0,2,,那就奇怪了\NThis is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.69,0:51:52.19,Default,,0,0,2,,This whole...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.69,0:51:55.86,Default,,0,0,2,,这…整件事实在太怪异\NThis whole thing is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.94,0:52:00.07,Default,,0,0,2,,那又何必去做呢？\NThen why go through with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.20,0:52:04.87,Default,,0,0,2,,故事很长\NIt's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.66,0:52:11.79,Default,,0,0,2,,而且很棒\NBut it's a really good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.87,0:52:13.96,Default,,0,0,2,,我会在车上告诉你\NI'll tell you on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.04,0:52:16.30,Default,,0,0,2,,看来我是摆脱不了你了\NI'm not going to get rid of you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.38,0:52:19.59,Default,,0,0,2,,只要你和我去看球赛\NCome to this game. I'll never bother you again, not even...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.59,0:52:20.59,Default,,0,0,2,,我发誓将来保证不再烦你 连圣诞卡也不会寄给你\N只要你和我去看球赛\NCome to this game. I'll never bother you again, not even...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.59,0:52:21.43,Default,,0,0,2,,我发誓将来保证不再烦你 连圣诞卡也不会寄给你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.43,0:52:23.47,Default,,0,0,2,,Not even a Christmas card.\N我发誓将来保证不再烦你 连圣诞卡也不会寄给你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.47,0:52:25.19,Default,,0,0,2,,我发誓将来保证不再烦你 连圣诞卡也不会寄给你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.44,0:52:34.48,Default,,0,0,2,,这些年来你都做些什么？\NSo what do you do with yourself these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.56,0:52:36.15,Default,,0,0,2,,我享受人生、努力工作\NI live, I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.90,0:52:38.74,Default,,0,0,2,,我学会了做菜\NI learned how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.90,0:52:41.49,Default,,0,0,2,,更爱边散步，边观赏落日\NI take walks and watch sunsets.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.95,0:52:45.28,Default,,0,0,2,,你难道不怀念过去的风光？\NDon't you miss being involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.37,0:52:48.41,Default,,0,0,2,,我曾是东岸混乱的批发商\NI was the East Coast distributor of involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.00,0:52:51.62,Default,,0,0,2,,随时在制造混乱\NI ate it and drank it and breathed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.87,0:52:55.08,Default,,0,0,2,,后来他们杀了马丁和巴比\NThen they killed Martin and Bobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.42,0:52:57.75,Default,,0,0,2,,而狡猾的尼克森又两度当选\Nthey elected Tricky Dick twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.92,0:52:59.67,Default,,0,0,2,,你以为我会因 往日的风光不再而痛不欲生？\Nand now people like you think
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.76,0:53:01.84,Default,,0,0,2,,I must be miserable because I'm not involved anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.92,0:53:03.80,Default,,0,0,2,,让我告诉你\NI've got news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.30,0:53:06.64,Default,,0,0,2,,以前的日子才悲惨\NI spent all my misery years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.97,0:53:09.18,Default,,0,0,2,,如今我不必为别人去努力\NI have no more pain left for any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.27,0:53:11.06,Default,,0,0,2,,只为自己而忙\NI gave at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.35,0:53:14.10,Default,,0,0,2,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.94,0:53:16.12,Default,,0,0,2,,好，你想要什么？\NI want them to stop looking to me for answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.12,0:53:17.61,Default,,0,0,2,,我要他们 别叫我去替他们寻找答案\N好，你想要什么？\NI want them to stop looking to me for answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.61,0:53:17.69,Default,,0,0,2,,我要他们 别叫我去替他们寻找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.69,0:53:18.64,Default,,0,0,2,,或要求我再开始演讲、写作 做他们的领导人\Nbegging me to speak again, write again, be a leader.\N我要他们 别叫我去替他们寻找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.64,0:53:20.94,Default,,0,0,2,,或要求我再开始演讲、写作 做他们的领导人\Nbegging me to speak again, write again, be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.03,0:53:23.45,Default,,0,0,2,,我要他们开始为自己思考\NI want them to start thinking for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.53,0:53:25.24,Default,,0,0,2,,我要有自己的私生活\NI want my privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.66,0:53:29.87,Default,,0,0,2,,不，我是问你想要什么？\NNo, I meant what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.79,0:53:38.25,Default,,0,0,2,,热狗和啤酒\NDog and a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.46,0:53:41.51,Default,,0,0,2,,来两份\NTwo.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.88,0:53:43.22,Default,,0,0,2,,一共十块钱\N10 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.01,0:53:45.89,Default,,0,0,2,,我了解你的想法\NOkay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.97,0:53:48.35,Default,,0,0,2,,你有权力拥有自己的私生活\NYou should be entitled to as much privacy as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.43,0:53:50.43,Default,,0,0,2,,可是为什么停止写作？\Nbut why stop writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.35,0:53:53.43,Default,,0,0,2,,十七年来我没出过一本书\NI haven't published a word in 17 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.52,0:53:56.35,Default,,0,0,2,,却仍要忍受你这种疯子\Nand still I have to endure lunatics like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.44,0:54:00.23,Default,,0,0,2,,你想若我突然出书 会发生什么情况？\NWhat do you think would happen if I suddenly came out with a new book?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.32,0:54:02.07,Default,,0,0,2,,他们会把我榨干的\NThey'd bleed me dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.29,0:54:18.63,Default,,0,0,2,,到远方去\NGo the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.72,0:54:29.01,Default,,0,0,2,,到远方去\NGo the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.71,0:54:34.64,Default,,0,0,2,,“艾契月光葛汉，明尼苏达 奇斯何姆，纽约巨人队”
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.71,0:54:38.20,Default,,0,0,2,,“终生资料 一场比赛——零打击”
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.87,0:54:50.49,Default,,0,0,2,,怎么了？\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.00,0:54:55.79,Default,,0,0,2,,你没看到？      看到什么？\NYou didn't see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.87,0:54:57.21,Default,,0,0,2,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.88,0:55:06.13,Default,,0,0,2,,对不起 我想你不必再待下去了\NI'm sorry. I guess you didn't have to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.22,0:55:07.34,Default,,0,0,2,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.72,0:55:13.22,Default,,0,0,2,,我们随时可以离开\NWhenever you want to go, we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.89,0:55:15.43,Default,,0,0,2,,好，那就走吧\NFine. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.94,0:56:04.36,Default,,0,0,2,,你到底在瞒着我什么？\NWhat is it you're not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.40,0:56:08.32,Default,,0,0,2,,我已经花去你太多时间\NI've already taken up too much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.46,0:56:22.71,Default,,0,0,2,,但愿我有你的激情\NI wish I had your passion, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.96,0:56:26.30,Default,,0,0,2,,虽然被误导，但仍是激情\NMisdirected though it might be, it is still a passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.63,0:56:29.51,Default,,0,0,2,,我曾经也像你一样，可是…\NI used to feel that way about things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.93,0:56:35.10,Default,,0,0,2,,你又收到讯息了吗？\NYou got another message, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.18,0:56:36.56,Default,,0,0,2,,你一定认为我疯了\NYou'll think I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.64,0:56:38.52,Default,,0,0,2,,我早就这么想了 是什么讯息？\NI already think you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.60,0:56:40.18,Default,,0,0,2,,What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.15,0:56:46.32,Default,,0,0,2,,它说“够了，别再打扰他”\NIt said, "The man's done enough. Leave him alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.88,0:57:08.63,Default,,0,0,2,,月光葛汉\N"Moonlight" Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.51,0:57:10.72,Default,,0,0,2,,你看到了      看到什么？\NYou saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.80,0:57:11.92,Default,,0,0,2,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.76,0:57:15.76,Default,,0,0,2,,你看到讯息了 1922年纽约巨人队\NYou saw it. New York Giants, 1922.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.85,0:57:18.31,Default,,0,0,2,,他只参加一场比赛 但没有击球，你看到了\NHe played one game. He never got to bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.39,0:57:21.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我看到什么啦？ 明尼苏达州的奇斯何姆\NWhat did I see? Chisholm, Minnesota.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.39,0:57:25.02,Default,,0,0,2,,我们是唯一看到它的人\NWe were the only ones who saw it. Did you hear the voice, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.10,0:57:26.30,Default,,0,0,2,,你有没有听到声音？\NIt's what told me to find you. Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.30,0:57:28.60,Default,,0,0,2,,你尽管承认 就是它让我来找你的\N你有没有听到声音？\NIt's what told me to find you. Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.60,0:57:28.67,Default,,0,0,2,,你有没有听到声音？\NIt's what told me to find you. Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.67,0:57:28.86,Default,,0,0,2,,你听到了吗？\N你有没有听到声音？\NIt's what told me to find you. Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.86,0:57:30.10,Default,,0,0,2,,你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.36,0:57:33.03,Default,,0,0,2,,“到远方去”\N"Go the distance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.11,0:57:36.99,Default,,0,0,2,,对！你知道是什么意思吗？\NYes. Do you know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.07,0:57:38.28,Default,,0,0,2,,知道      什么意思？\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.37,0:57:39.49,Default,,0,0,2,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.58,0:57:42.71,Default,,0,0,2,,它叫我们到明尼苏达州 去找月光葛汉\NIt means we're going to Minnesota to find "Moonlight" Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.79,0:57:44.46,Default,,0,0,2,,我们？你说我们吗？\NWe're going... We?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.54,0:57:46.17,Default,,0,0,2,,我一定也疯了\NI must be out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.25,0:57:48.63,Default,,0,0,2,,找到他后怎么办？\NWhat do we do when we find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.71,0:57:51.05,Default,,0,0,2,,我怎么会晓得\NHow the hell am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.13,0:57:53.88,Default,,0,0,2,,没错，一点也没错\NThat's right. You're right. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.63,0:57:56.09,Default,,0,0,2,,太不可思议了 真不相信我也会这么疯\NThis is so bitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.18,0:57:58.01,Default,,0,0,2,,I don't believe I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.24,0:58:19.37,Default,,0,0,2,,嘿，安妮 我现在和泰伦斯孟在一起\NHey, Annie, guess what? I'm with Terence Mann.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.45,0:58:21.54,Default,,0,0,2,,天呀，你绑架他了\NOh, my God. You kidnapped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.62,0:58:24.33,Default,,0,0,2,,No, I didn't. He wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.41,0:58:25.61,Default,,0,0,2,,没有，他是自愿的\NSorry, but I'm going to be a few days longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.61,0:58:27.17,Default,,0,0,2,,对不起，我得再多待几天\N没有，他是自愿的\NSorry, but I'm going to be a few days longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.17,0:58:27.79,Default,,0,0,2,,对不起，我得再多待几天
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.79,0:58:28.87,Default,,0,0,2,,我们要去明尼苏达州 真的吗？\N- We're going to Minnesota. - I don't believe this.\N对不起，我得再多待几天
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.87,0:58:30.38,Default,,0,0,2,,我们要去明尼苏达州 真的吗？\N- We're going to Minnesota. - I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.46,0:58:32.09,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么去明尼苏达呢？ 为了一个老球员\NWhat's in Minnesota?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.17,0:58:35.01,Default,,0,0,2,,An old ballplayer. I'll explain when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.09,0:58:36.93,Default,,0,0,2,,等回家后再解释\NHow are things with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.01,0:58:38.26,Default,,0,0,2,,你那边都好吧？\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.34,0:58:40.09,Default,,0,0,2,,很好      那就好\NGreat. Look, Ann, I got to go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.09,0:58:40.76,Default,,0,0,2,,我得挂电话了\N很好      那就好\NGreat. Look, Ann, I got to go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.76,0:58:41.68,Default,,0,0,2,,我得挂电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.68,0:58:42.78,Default,,0,0,2,,替我抱抱凯伦，还有我爱你\NGive Karin a hug for me,\N我得挂电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.78,0:58:43.64,Default,,0,0,2,,替我抱抱凯伦，还有我爱你\NGive Karin a hug for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.18,0:58:45.27,Default,,0,0,2,,and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.77,0:58:47.02,Default,,0,0,2,,我也爱你\NI love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.10,0:58:50.36,Default,,0,0,2,,将来你一定要解释清楚好吗？\NHey, someday explain all this to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.44,0:58:51.86,Default,,0,0,2,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.94,0:58:53.07,Default,,0,0,2,,我会尽量的，再见\NBye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.15,0:58:54.15,Default,,0,0,2,,再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.45,0:59:03.41,Default,,0,0,2,,你为什么不告诉他？\NWhy didn't you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.71,0:59:07.22,Default,,0,0,2,,Annie, you got no choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.22,0:59:08.33,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，你现在毫无选择\NAnnie, you got no choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.33,0:59:09.38,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，你现在毫无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.62,0:59:12.49,Default,,0,0,2,,“奇斯何姆百年纪念日”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.21,0:59:15.05,Default,,0,0,2,,一堆姓葛汉的人\NHalf a dozen Grahams.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.13,0:59:17.80,Default,,0,0,2,,就是没有艾契或月光\NNo Archibald. No "Moonlight."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.59,0:59:20.93,Default,,0,0,2,,跟我来\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.47,0:59:26.41,Default,,0,0,2,,“论坛报”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.98,0:59:34.15,Default,,0,0,2,,哈啰\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.69,0:59:37.61,Default,,0,0,2,,我们想请你帮个忙\NExcuse me. Maybe you can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.70,0:59:41.07,Default,,0,0,2,,我们在找前棒球员艾契葛汉\NWe're looking for an ex-baseball player named Archibald Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.16,0:59:42.45,Default,,0,0,2,,喔，你是指葛汉医生\NYou mean Doc Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.53,0:59:45.08,Default,,0,0,2,,不，他的绰号是月光\NNo. I think his nickname was "Moonlight."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.16,0:59:46.45,Default,,0,0,2,,那就是葛汉医生\NWell, that's Dr. Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.54,0:59:48.04,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉医生？\NDr. Graham?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.12,0:59:50.42,Default,,0,0,2,,他的棒球生涯一直没多大发展 所以又回学校念书\NHis baseball career never amounted to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.50,0:59:52.33,Default,,0,0,2,,He went back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.59,0:59:54.00,Default,,0,0,2,,他父亲是个医生 我们怎么才能找到他\NHis father was a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:55.55,Default,,0,0,2,,Do you know where we can find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.63,0:59:58.84,Default,,0,0,2,,放心，我们不是税务局的人\NIt's nothing bad. We're not from the IRS.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.05,1:00:01.84,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉医生已经死了\NDoc Graham is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.01,1:00:04.01,Default,,0,0,2,,他死于1972年\NHe died in 1972.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.02,1:00:09.10,Default,,0,0,2,,“曾经有段时间人们无法负担”\N"And there were times when children could not afford
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.19,1:00:11.52,Default,,0,0,2,,“孩子们的眼镜、牛奶或衣服”\N"eyeglasses or milk or clothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.02,1:00:14.94,Default,,0,0,2,,“然而他们却从不缺乏这些”\N"Yet, no child was ever denied these essentials
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.02,1:00:18.32,Default,,0,0,2,,“全是因为葛汉医生的原故”\N"because, in the background, there was always Dr. Graham.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.40,1:00:20.78,Default,,0,0,2,,“他不为虚名”\N"Without any fanfare or publicity,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.86,1:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,2,,“只是默默的把眼镜、牛奶 或是球赛的票”\N"the glasses or the milk or the ticket to the ballgame
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.70,1:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,2,,“悄悄的放到孩子们的衣袋里”\N"found their way into the child's pocket."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.08,1:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,2,,You wrote that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.33,1:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,2,,是你写的\NThe day he died.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.62,1:00:33.04,Default,,0,0,2,,就在他死的那一天 我能看吗？\NCan I see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.13,1:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,2,,你是个好作家\NYou're a good writer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.88,1:00:36.25,Default,,0,0,2,,你也一样\NSo are you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.34,1:00:44.09,Default,,0,0,2,,到底缺了什么？\NSomething's missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.89,1:00:48.72,Default,,0,0,2,,听起来他是个大好人\NWell, he sounds like he was a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.93,1:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,2,,在北部有一堆葛汉医生\NHalf the towns in North America have a Doc Graham.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.81,1:00:57.65,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么在死后十六年\NWhat makes this one so special we travel across the country to find him
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.73,1:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,2,,居然让我们 横越半个大陆来找他\N16 years after he died?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.71,1:00:59.61,Default,,0,0,2,,他到底有什么特殊？\N居然让我们 横越半个大陆来找他\N16 years after he died?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.61,1:01:00.64,Default,,0,0,2,,他到底有什么特殊？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.74,1:01:02.40,Default,,0,0,2,,一定有别的原因\NThere's got to be more.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.66,1:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,2,,还有什么？\NWhat else?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.29,1:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,2,,他永远都穿着大衣\NHe always wore an overcoat,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.83,1:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,2,,一头白发，手里拿着雨伞\Nhe had white hair,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.75,1:01:16.75,Default,,0,0,2,,and he always carried an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.84,1:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么要拿雨伞？ 我想是一种习惯\NWhat was the umbrella for?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.38,1:01:21.88,Default,,0,0,2,,It got to be a habit, something to hang on to.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.97,1:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,2,,让手上握着点东西\NHe said he used it to beat away his lady admirers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.07,1:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,2,,如果问他，他会说 是为了赶走那些女性爱慕者\N让手上握着点东西\NHe said he used it to beat away his lady admirers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.72,1:01:26.39,Default,,0,0,2,,如果问他，他会说 是为了赶走那些女性爱慕者
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.39,1:01:27.37,Default,,0,0,2,,那他的太太呢？\NTell me about his wife.\N如果问他，他会说 是为了赶走那些女性爱慕者
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.37,1:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,2,,那他的太太呢？\NTell me about his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.56,1:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,2,,爱丽莎\NAlicia.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.27,1:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,2,,在葛汉医生过逝后\NShe moved to South Carolina after Doc passed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.82,1:01:35.27,Default,,0,0,2,,她搬到南卡罗来纳州\N在葛汉医生过逝后\NShe moved to South Carolina after Doc passed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.27,1:01:36.73,Default,,0,0,2,,她搬到南卡罗来纳州
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.73,1:01:37.75,Default,,0,0,2,,几年后也去逝了\NShe passed a couple years later.\N她搬到南卡罗来纳州
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.75,1:01:38.94,Default,,0,0,2,,几年后也去逝了\NShe passed a couple years later.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.86,1:01:41.78,Default,,0,0,2,,她喜欢戴蓝帽子\NShe always wore blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.20,1:01:47.41,Default,,0,0,2,,城里的店主们\NThe shopkeepers in town would stock blue hats
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.91,1:01:49.03,Default,,0,0,2,,会买许多蓝帽子\Nbecause they knew if Doc walked by, he'd buy one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.03,1:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,2,,因为他们知道如果医生看到了\N会买许多蓝帽子\Nbecause they knew if Doc walked by, he'd buy one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.37,1:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,2,,会买许多蓝帽子\Nbecause they knew if Doc walked by, he'd buy one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.44,1:01:52.62,Default,,0,0,2,,一定会买\N会买许多蓝帽子\Nbecause they knew if Doc walked by, he'd buy one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.62,1:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,2,,一定会买
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.62,1:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,2,,当他们打扫他诊所时\NWhen they cleaned out his office,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.46,1:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,2,,找到一堆全新的蓝帽子\Nthey found boxes of blue hats
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.01,1:02:04.63,Default,,0,0,2,,还没来得及送给她前就死了\Nthat he never got around to give her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.38,1:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,2,,这事你一定不知道\NI'll bet you didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.89,1:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,2,,是不知道\NNo, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.93,1:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,2,,他不滥交、不酗酒\NNo screwing, no drinking, no opium, no midnight abortions,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.26,1:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,2,,不抽大麻、不替人堕胎\N他不滥交、不酗酒\NNo screwing, no drinking, no opium, no midnight abortions,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.40,1:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,2,,不抽大麻、不替人堕胎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.90,1:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,2,,没有私生子\Nno illegitimate children,\N不抽大麻、不替人堕胎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.06,1:02:20.90,Default,,0,0,2,,没有私生子\Nno illegitimate children,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.28,1:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,2,,也没有财务危机\Nno shady finances.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.32,1:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,2,,你好像很失望\NYou sound disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.49,1:02:29.74,Default,,0,0,2,,赤脚乔他有问题 所以才需要你\NShoeless Joe had a problem. That's why he needed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.37,1:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,2,,可是他根本不需要我们\NThis guy doesn't need us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.16,1:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,2,,泰伦斯\NTerence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.37,1:02:38.50,Default,,0,0,2,,你知道你失踪了吗？\NDo you know you're missing?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.96,1:02:44.17,Default,,0,0,2,,啊！我的天\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.63,1:02:47.97,Default,,0,0,2,,“他那住在巴尔的摩的父亲”\N"His father, who lives in Baltimore,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.05,1:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,2,,“在打了数通无人接的电话后 已向警方报案”\N"notified police after receiving no answer to repeated telephone calls."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.01,1:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,2,,糟糕，我最好打电话给他\NShoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.18,1:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,2,,I better call him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.77,1:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,2,,要不要我…\NYou want me to...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.52,1:02:58.81,Default,,0,0,2,,谢谢你\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.19,1:03:07.78,Default,,0,0,2,,我出去散步，等会儿回来\NI'm taking a walk. Be back in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.70,1:03:15.37,Default,,0,0,2,,我该怎么对他说？\NWhat do I tell him?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.24,1:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,2,,“艾咪咖啡店”
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.75,1:03:36.18,Default,,0,0,2,,“四年后重选总统”
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.32,1:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,2,,“教父，今年排行前十名”
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.32,1:03:44.82,Default,,0,0,2,,“今年”\N"This year's"?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.44,1:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉医生？\NDr. Graham?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.83,1:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉医生？\NDr. Graham?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.62,1:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,2,,我是从爱荷华来的瑞康斯拉\NMy name's Ray Kinsella. I'm from Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.55,1:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,2,,你是月光葛汉吗？\NAre you "Moonlight" Graham?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.35,1:04:58.47,Default,,0,0,2,,已经五十年没人这么叫我了\NNo one's called me "Moonlight" Graham in 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.23,1:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,2,,我是从很远的地方来看你\NWell, I've come a very long way to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.65,1:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,2,,通常我睡得像小孩一样 可是今晚却睡不着\NI couldn't sleep tonight. Usually I sleep like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.19,1:05:09.65,Default,,0,0,2,,所以告诉爱丽莎我要出来散步\NI told Alicia I was taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.86,1:05:13.95,Default,,0,0,2,,我能和你一起散步吗？ 我很想和你聊聊\NDo you mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.11,1:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,2,,I'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.66,1:05:18.87,Default,,0,0,2,,那一起到我诊所去\NLet's walk over to my office.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.66,1:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,2,,你想和我聊什么？\NWhat do you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.87,1:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,2,,当你参加巨人队时 只打了一局\NWhen you got to the majors, you played only one inning of one game.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.88,1:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,2,,怎么会那样？\NWhat happened that inning?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.84,1:05:32.13,Default,,0,0,2,,那是季赛的最后一天\NIt was the last day of the season,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.22,1:05:34.68,Default,,0,0,2,,第八局的后半局 我们远远超过对方\Nbottom of the eighth, we were way ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.76,1:05:38.39,Default,,0,0,2,,我参加巨人队大约三个礼拜 但没什么刺激的比赛\NIn three weeks, I hadn't seen any action.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.14,1:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,2,,突然约翰麦格罗指着我的方向\NSuddenly old John McGraw points a bony finger in my direction
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.60,1:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,2,,说“右野”\Nand he says, "Right field."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.77,1:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,2,,我像从弹簧上弹起来一样\NI jumped up like I was sitting on a spring,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.44,1:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,2,,抓起手套立刻跑向右野\Ngrabbed my glove, and ran out on the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.03,1:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,2,,你有任何表现吗？\NDid you get to make a play?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.37,1:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,2,,可惜球一直没打到外野来\NThey never hit the ball out of the infield.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.79,1:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,2,,比赛结束，季赛也完了\NThe game ended. The season was over.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.12,1:06:07.54,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道他们不会要我\NI knew they'd send me back down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.00,1:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,2,,而我不愿意再花一年的时间 做乙等球队的队员\NI couldn't bear the thought of another year in the minors.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.42,1:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,2,,所以决定放弃棒球\NSo I decided to hang them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.89,1:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,2,,请坐\NGo on. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.14,1:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,2,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.89,1:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,2,,那你有什么感觉？\NSo what was that like?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.89,1:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,2,,就差这么一点，梦想就能实现\NIt was like coming this close to your dreams,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.31,1:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,2,,但它却像陌生人般的 和你擦身而过\Nthen watch them brush past you, like a stranger in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.40,1:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,2,,当初并没有这种感觉\NThen, you don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.32,1:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,2,,我们往往不能认清 一生中的关键时刻\NWe just don't recognize life's most significant moments
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.24,1:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,2,,while they're happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.41,1:06:42.74,Default,,0,0,2,,那时我常说“以后还有机会”\NBack then I thought, "Well, there'll be other days."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.25,1:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,2,,却没料到那是唯一的机会\NI didn't realize that that was the only day.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.96,1:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,2,,And now, I want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.63,1:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，我现在想问你个问题\NAnd now, I want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.09,1:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，我现在想问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.09,1:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,2,,是什么动机让你在五十年后\NWhat's so interesting about half an inning that you'd come from Iowa\N瑞，我现在想问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.30,1:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,2,,是什么动机让你在五十年后\NWhat's so interesting about half an inning that you'd come from Iowa
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.59,1:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,2,,大老远的从爱荷华到这里来\Nto talk to me about it 50 years after it happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.94,1:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,2,,和我谈那半局的比赛呢？\N大老远的从爱荷华到这里来\Nto talk to me about it 50 years after it happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.85,1:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,2,,和我谈那半局的比赛呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.14,1:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,2,,老实说，到现在我才知道原因 我想该这么问你\NI didn't really know till just now,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.68,1:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,2,,but I think it's to ask you if you could do anything you wanted,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.25,1:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你能做任何你想做的事\Nbut I think it's to ask you if you could do anything you wanted,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.69,1:07:08.98,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你能做任何你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.98,1:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你能让梦想成真\Nif you could have a wish...\N如果你能做任何你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.15,1:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你能让梦想成真\Nif you could have a wish...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.19,1:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,2,,而你就是 能使我梦想成真的人？\NAnd you're the kind of a man who could grant me that wish?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.87,1:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,2,,只是问问，我不能确定\NI don't know. I'm just asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.12,1:07:25.70,Default,,0,0,2,,你是知道的…\NWell, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.46,1:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,2,,我没有在职业棒球赛中击过球\NI never got to bat in the major leagues.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.71,1:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,2,,所以希望有一天能有机会\NI'd have liked to have had that chance, just once,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.92,1:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,2,,用眼睛盯着那一流的投手\Nto stare down a big-league pitcher.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.25,1:07:38.59,Default,,0,0,2,,盯着他直到他挥臂准备投球 然后一眨眼\NThen just as he goes into his windup, wink.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.01,1:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,2,,让他以为我看出什么破绽\NMake him think you know something he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.64,1:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,2,,我的梦想就是 眯着眼看着天空\NThat's what I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.64,1:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,2,,The chance to squint at a sky so blue it hurts your eyes to look at it,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.68,1:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,2,,它蓝得那么刺眼\Nto feel the tingle in your arms as you connect with the ball,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.90,1:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,2,,在击球时臂膀刺痛的感觉\N它蓝得那么刺眼\Nto feel the tingle in your arms as you connect with the ball,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.52,1:07:50.60,Default,,0,0,2,,在击球时臂膀刺痛的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.60,1:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,2,,跑垒时，为了盗垒\Nrun bases, stretching a double into a triple and flop face first into third,\N在击球时臂膀刺痛的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.77,1:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,2,,跑垒时，为了盗垒\Nrun bases, stretching a double into a triple and flop face first into third,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.98,1:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,2,,脸先着地的扑向垒包\Nwrap your arms around the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.70,1:08:00.01,Default,,0,0,2,,伸长手臂去触摸垒包\NThat's my wish. That's my wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.01,1:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,2,,那是我的梦想 瑞，那就是我的梦想\N伸长手臂去触摸垒包\NThat's my wish. That's my wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.37,1:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,2,,那是我的梦想 瑞，那就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.66,1:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,2,,在这月光之下 真有那神奇的力量\NIs there enough magic out there in the moonlight
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.66,1:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,2,,能让我的梦想成真吗？\Nto make this dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.21,1:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,2,,如果我说能，你信吗？\NWhat would you say if I said yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.13,1:08:15.50,Default,,0,0,2,,我还真会相信你\NI think I'd actually believe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.88,1:08:19.30,Default,,0,0,2,,那么有一个地方 能让你的梦想成真\NThere's a place where things like that happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.38,1:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,2,,如果你愿意，我可以带你去\NIf you want to go, I can take you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.68,1:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,2,,对我来说 这里是全世界最特殊的地方\NThis is my most special place in all the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.35,1:08:33.42,Default,,0,0,2,,它对我的影响非常大\NOnce a place touches you like this, the wind never blows so cold again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.42,1:08:34.52,Default,,0,0,2,,让我感觉不到风的冰冷\N它对我的影响非常大\NOnce a place touches you like this, the wind never blows so cold again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.52,1:08:35.85,Default,,0,0,2,,让我感觉不到风的冰冷
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.86,1:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,2,,它就像我的小孩一样\NYou feel for it, like it was your child.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.24,1:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,2,,我不能离开奇斯何姆\NI can't leave Chisholm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.82,1:08:46.45,Default,,0,0,2,,我了解\NI understand. I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.80,1:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,2,,真的了解
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.91,1:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,2,,可是我仍旧认为 你应该和我们一起去\NBut I really think you're supposed to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.50,1:08:54.54,Default,,0,0,2,,可是我仍旧认为 你应该和我们一起去\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.21,1:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,2,,可是你的梦想呢？\NBut your wish?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.72,1:09:02.76,Default,,0,0,2,,就继续做梦吧！\NIt'll have to stay a wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.93,1:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,2,,我生在这儿、长在这儿\NI was born here, I lived here, I'll die here, but no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.46,1:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,2,,也要死在这儿，绝不后悔\N我生在这儿、长在这儿\NI was born here, I lived here, I'll die here, but no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.60,1:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,2,,也要死在这儿，绝不后悔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.39,1:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,2,,在五十年前 有五分钟你的梦想几乎实现\NFifty years ago, for 5 minutes you came this close.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.89,1:09:14.52,Default,,0,0,2,,It would kill some men
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.60,1:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,2,,有人会为错过举手可得的机会 而顿足捶胸\Nto get that close to their dream and not touch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.73,1:09:20.65,Default,,0,0,2,,甚至把它当成一场悲剧\NGod. They'd consider it a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.74,1:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,2,,孩子，反过来看 如果做医生是我那没实现的梦\NIf I'd only gotten to be a doctor for five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.74,1:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,2,,now that would have been a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.25,1:09:27.24,Default,,0,0,2,,我认为那才是真正的悲剧\Nnow that would have been a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.24,1:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,2,,我认为那才是真正的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.91,1:09:34.06,Default,,0,0,2,,我得回家了\NI better be getting home. Alicia will think I got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.06,1:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,2,,否则爱丽莎以为我有女朋友了\N我得回家了\NI better be getting home. Alicia will think I got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.42,1:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,2,,否则爱丽莎以为我有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.25,1:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,2,,然后他笑了\NAnd he smiled.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.92,1:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,2,,后来我想…\NAnd then I figured, maybe we're not supposed to take him with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.90,1:09:43.88,Default,,0,0,2,,也许我们根本不该带他走\N后来我想…\NAnd then I figured, maybe we're not supposed to take him with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.88,1:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,2,,也许我们根本不该带他走
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.63,1:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,2,,我真的不懂\NI don't know.\N也许我们根本不该带他走
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.89,1:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,2,,我真的不懂\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.10,1:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,2,,现在好啦 为什么要我们来这里呢\NI don't know why in the hell we were supposed to come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.18,1:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,2,,也许是来探讨 一局比赛能否改变世界\NMaybe it's to find out if one inning can change the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.90,1:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,2,,能吗？ 的确曾改变过一些人\NThink it did?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.02,1:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,2,,Did for these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.86,1:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,2,,如果他击过球 或许就会留在棒球队里\NIf he'd gotten a hit, he might have stayed in baseball.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.07,1:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,2,,我也搞不清\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.28,1:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,2,,你太太打过电话来\NYour wife called. She wants you to call her tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.37,1:10:08.66,Default,,0,0,2,,她要你今晚打电话回去\N你太太打过电话来\NYour wife called. She wants you to call her tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.66,1:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,2,,她要你今晚打电话回去
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.29,1:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,2,,是瑞吗？\NRay?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.00,1:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,2,,我很好，真高兴是你\NI'm fine. I'm just so glad it's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.34,1:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,2,,我和银行谈过\NListen, I talked to the bank,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.01,1:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,2,,并且问他们 可不可以迟付几个月\Nand I asked them if we could miss a payment or two,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.84,1:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,2,,他们说已经把农场的借据\Nand they told me that they had just sold the note on the farm
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.14,1:10:35.27,Default,,0,0,2,,卖给马克和他的合伙人\Nto Mark and his partners.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.65,1:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,2,,所以他们是债权人了\NRight. So they own the paper now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.48,1:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,2,,他说若不卖给他们 农场就会被拍卖\NHe says if we don't sell to them, they're going to foreclose.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.94,1:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,2,,我们现在一点钱也没有\NRay, we don't have the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.28,1:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,2,,好，我计划…\NLook, I've got to take Mr. Mann back to Boston first.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.45,1:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,2,,先送泰伦斯孟回波士顿\NOkay? So, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.49,1:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,2,,所以要…\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.66,1:10:56.16,Default,,0,0,2,,不\NWait a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.67,1:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,2,,你等一下\NI'm going to Iowa with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.25,1:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,2,,我和你一起回爱荷华\N你等一下\NI'm going to Iowa with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.75,1:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,2,,我和你一起回爱荷华
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.09,1:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,2,,我们马上回家\NWe're coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.26,1:11:10.97,Default,,0,0,2,,我现在绝不能放弃\NHell, I can't quit now. I got to see this ballpark.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.68,1:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,2,,一定要看看这个球场\NNot everyone can see it. You might not.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.80,1:11:14.14,Default,,0,0,2,,并不是人人都能看到 也许你就看不到\N一定要看看这个球场\NNot everyone can see it. You might not.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.14,1:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,2,,并不是人人都能看到 也许你就看不到
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.18,1:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,2,,总得去试试\NGive it a try.\N并不是人人都能看到 也许你就看不到
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.82,1:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,2,,总得去试试\NGive it a try.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.11,1:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,2,,从现在起我得要多积阴德\NI need all the karma I can get right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.70,1:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,2,,谢谢，你是第一辆车\NThanks. You're the first car by.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.87,1:11:34.87,Default,,0,0,2,,你到哪里去？ 你们要去哪里呢？\NHow far you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.95,1:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,2,,How far you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.20,1:11:37.33,Default,,0,0,2,,爱荷华\NIowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.71,1:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,2,,那我能不能和你们走一段\NIf it's okay, I'll just ride along a while. I play baseball.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.53,1:11:41.54,Default,,0,0,2,,我是打棒球的\N那我能不能和你们走一段\NIf it's okay, I'll just ride along a while. I play baseball.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.54,1:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,2,,我是打棒球的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.59,1:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,2,,上车吧      谢谢\NHop in. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.22,1:11:55.85,Default,,0,0,2,,我想找个地方打球 听说在中西部很多城市\NI'm looking for a place to play.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.93,1:11:59.81,Default,,0,0,2,,I heard that all through the Midwest, they have towns with teams.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.90,1:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,2,,都有自己的球队\NIn some places, they'll find you a day job
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.05,1:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,2,,有些球队 甚至会替你找份白天的工作\N都有自己的球队\NIn some places, they'll find you a day job
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.15,1:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,2,,有些球队 甚至会替你找份白天的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.23,1:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,2,,好让你在晚上或周末打球\Nso you can play ball nights and weekends.\N有些球队 甚至会替你找份白天的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.11,1:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,2,,好让你在晚上或周末打球\Nso you can play ball nights and weekends.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.82,1:12:09.49,Default,,0,0,2,,你运气真好 我们就是去那种地方\NIt's your lucky day. We're going someplace kind of like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.03,1:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,2,,太棒了！\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.49,1:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,2,,我是瑞康斯拉 这位是泰伦斯孟\NI'm Ray Kinsella. This is Terence Mann.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.29,1:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,2,,你们好\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.08,1:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,2,,我叫艾契葛汉\NI'm Archie Graham.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.43,1:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,2,,奇怪他所形容的那种 参加他们的球队\NIt's funny the way he described towns finding you a job
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.89,1:12:37.18,Default,,0,0,2,,就替你找工作的那件事\Nso you could play on their team.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.43,1:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,2,,已经停止很久了\NThey haven't done that for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.81,1:12:42.98,Default,,0,0,2,,我父亲曾经参加过 但那是贰零年代的事\NDad did that for a while, but that was in the '20s.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.11,1:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,2,,你父亲后来怎么了？\NWhat happened to your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.40,1:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,2,,他棒球生涯一直没有成就 只好将希望寄托在儿子身上\NHe never made it as a ballplayer. He wanted his son to make it for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.40,1:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,2,,在我十岁时，打棒球就像\NBy 10, playing baseball got to be like eating vegetables or taking out garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.85,1:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,2,,吃蔬菜、倒垃圾那么平常\N在我十岁时，打棒球就像\NBy 10, playing baseball got to be like eating vegetables or taking out garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.33,1:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,2,,吃蔬菜、倒垃圾那么平常
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.58,1:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,2,,可是到了十四岁我开始拒绝\NWhen I was 14, I started to refuse.\N吃蔬菜、倒垃圾那么平常
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.65,1:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,2,,可是到了十四岁我开始拒绝\NWhen I was 14, I started to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.71,1:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,2,,你能相信吗？\NCan you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.63,1:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,2,,美国小男孩 居然不愿意和父亲玩接球\NAmerican boy refusing to have a catch with his father?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.13,1:13:08.42,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么在十四岁？\NWhy 14?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.55,1:13:13.05,Default,,0,0,2,,因为我刚看完泰伦斯孟 那本“摇篮般的小船”\NThat's when I read The Boat Rocker by Terence Mann.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.13,1:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,2,,哟，天呀 从此不再和他玩接球\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.30,1:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,2,,I never played catch with him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.22,1:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,2,,我怎么会那么倒楣 你不要和父亲玩球\NThat's the crap people always lay on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.97,1:13:21.10,Default,,0,0,2,,又不是我的错\NIt's not my fault you wouldn't play catch with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.18,1:13:22.39,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.40,1:13:27.27,Default,,0,0,2,,后来，到了十七岁\NAnyway, when I was 17,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.61,1:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,2,,我把行李一装 说了些狠话就走了\NI packed my things, said something awful, and left.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.86,1:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,2,,过了一段时间 想回家却不知该怎么做\NAfter a while, I wanted to come home, but I didn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.53,1:13:40.12,Default,,0,0,2,,最后只去参加他的葬礼\NMade it back for the funeral, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.55,1:13:53.01,Default,,0,0,2,,你说了什么狠话？\NWhat was the awful thing you said?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.51,1:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,2,,对你的父亲？\NTo your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.51,1:14:03.31,Default,,0,0,2,,我说我无法尊敬 一个把罪犯视为英雄的人\NI said I could never respect a man whose hero was a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.02,1:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,2,,他的英雄是谁？\NWho was his hero?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.52,1:14:09.36,Default,,0,0,2,,赤脚乔杰克森\NShoeless Joe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.86,1:14:14.07,Default,,0,0,2,,你应该知道他并不是罪犯\NYou knew he wasn't a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.70,1:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么你要那么说？\NThen why did you say it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.03,1:14:19.28,Default,,0,0,2,,我才十七岁呀\NI was 17.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.62,1:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,2,,在我能收回这句话之前 他就去逝了\NThe son of a bitch died before I could take it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.21,1:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,2,,在我能告诉他…\NBefore I could tell him,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.71,1:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,2,,你知道的\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.72,1:14:37.55,Default,,0,0,2,,他从没见过我太太\NHe never met my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.30,1:14:41.60,Default,,0,0,2,,也没见过他的孙女\NHe never saw his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.52,1:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,2,,你是为了赎罪\NThis is your penance.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.89,1:14:47.06,Default,,0,0,2,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.56,1:14:49.52,Default,,0,0,2,,我不能让父亲复活\NI can't bring my father back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.61,1:14:52.61,Default,,0,0,2,,所以至少让他的英雄回来\NSo the least you can do is bring back his hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.07,1:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,2,,这…\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.16,1:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,2,,大家来这里的目的都已明白\NNow I know what everybody's purpose here is,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.74,1:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,2,,除了我之外\Nexcept mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.25,1:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,2,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.78,1:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地！      凯伦，给爹地抱抱\NDaddy!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.03,1:15:38.61,Default,,0,0,2,,Karin, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.28,1:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨！\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.79,1:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,2,,We missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.95,1:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,2,,我们很想念你，你还好吧？\NAre you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.29,1:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,2,,好，这位是泰伦斯孟\NYeah. This is Terence Mann.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.29,1:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,2,,请叫我泰瑞\NTerry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.71,1:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,2,,欢迎你来   谢谢你\NWelcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.96,1:15:53.13,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，泰瑞\NHi, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.80,1:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,2,,这个年轻人是艾契葛汉\NAnd this young fella is... This is Archie Graham.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.22,1:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨\NArchie.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.09,1:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,2,,他是来和球队练球的\NHe's come to practice with the team.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.89,1:16:02.63,Default,,0,0,2,,He'll be able to do a lot more than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.63,1:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,2,,现在可不止练球而已了 你这是什么意思？\NHe'll be able to do a lot more than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.68,1:16:04.39,Default,,0,0,2,,现在可不止练球而已了 你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.39,1:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,2,,What does that mean?\N现在可不止练球而已了 你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.52,1:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,2,,现在可不止练球而已了 你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.87,1:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,2,,好啦，快来打球吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.81,1:16:15.11,Default,,0,0,2,,What do you say? What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.86,1:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,2,,你怎么说？\NHey, Ray. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.08,1:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，瑞\N你怎么说？\NHey, Ray. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.24,1:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,2,,你怎么说？\NHey, Ray. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.07,1:16:20.16,Default,,0,0,2,,你终于回来了\NThanks, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.24,1:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,2,,谢谢你，乔 我的天！\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.49,1:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,2,,怎么了？ 那是赤脚乔杰克森\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.62,1:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,2,,That's Shoeless Joe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.74,1:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,2,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.16,1:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,2,,当然是他，你居然不相信我\NYou didn't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.62,1:16:29.16,Default,,0,0,2,,我本来相信，可是…\NI thought I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.50,1:16:30.87,Default,,0,0,2,,噢，天呐！\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.54,1:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，安妮      嗨，乔\NHi, Annie. Hi, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.59,1:16:36.17,Default,,0,0,2,,很高兴见到你      我也是\NGood to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.63,1:16:39.92,Default,,0,0,2,,泰瑞，这位是赤脚乔杰克森\NTerry, I'd like you to meet Shoeless Joe Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.01,1:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,2,,乔，这位是泰伦斯孟\NJoe, Terry Mann.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.22,1:16:44.55,Default,,0,0,2,,真是我天大的荣幸 不，是我的荣幸\NIt's a pleasure meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.64,1:16:45.72,Default,,0,0,2,,The pleasure's mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.56,1:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，希望你不介意 我们练球练烦了\NWe got tired of just having practices,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.06,1:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,2,,所以把另一队叫来 好能来场真正的比赛\Nso we brought another team out so we'd have some real games.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.15,1:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,2,,不介意，他们从哪来的？\NI don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.27,1:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,2,,Where'd they come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.53,1:16:59.11,Default,,0,0,2,,我们又从哪来呢？\NWhere did we come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.19,1:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,2,,好多人争着要来这里打球\NSo many wanted to play here. We had to beat them off with a stick.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.57,1:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,2,,我们得用棍子打散他们\NHey, that's Smokey Joe Wood
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.12,1:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,2,,哇，那是红袜队的史莫基\Nand Mel Ott
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.83,1:17:10.29,Default,,0,0,2,,全垒王欧特和红雀队的哈吉斯\Nand Gil Hodges.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.37,1:17:12.29,Default,,0,0,2,,泰柯布也想来\NTy Cobb wanted to play.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.37,1:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,2,,可惜我们当时都不喜欢他\NNobody could stand him when we were alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.63,1:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,2,,所以就叫他滚到一边去\NWe told him to stick it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.76,1:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,2,,Hey, are you Graham?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.34,1:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,2,,你是葛汉？      是的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.89,1:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么站在那边 你不是来打球的吗？\NWhy are you on the sidelines? Came to play ball, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.93,1:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,2,,是的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.06,1:17:33.14,Default,,0,0,2,,那去暖身吧\NAll right. Well, go warm up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.94,1:17:35.15,Default,,0,0,2,,是的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.32,1:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,2,,这些新手\NRookies.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.57,1:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,2,,真难以置信\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.74,1:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,2,,你的形容还不够贴切\NIt's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.45,1:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,2,,是完美\NIt's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.38,1:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,2,,- Ho! - Safe!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.16,1:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,2,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.60,1:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉加油，来支安打\NGo, Graham! Go, kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.10,1:18:14.73,Default,,0,0,2,,加油，葛汉\NCome on, Archie!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.85,1:18:17.19,Default,,0,0,2,,和他们一比他就像个小婴孩\NHe looks like a baby next to those guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.27,1:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,2,,他是个小孩\NHe is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.86,1:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,2,,打个安打\NLet's get a hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.57,1:18:27.78,Default,,0,0,2,,快点呀\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.71,1:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,2,,小心\NWatch it, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.37,1:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,2,,喂，太过份啦\NSay hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.00,1:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,2,,别被他吓到，不要气馁\NDon't let him shake you up. Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.88,1:18:43.80,Default,,0,0,2,,你为什么要往他身上招呼\NKnuckles, what did you throw at the kid for?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.47,1:18:46.05,Default,,0,0,2,,他对我眨眼   孩子，别眨眼\NHe winked at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.26,1:18:47.80,Default,,0,0,2,,Don't wink, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.30,1:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,2,,Good thing for you he didn't throw the fastball.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.81,1:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,2,,好在他没投快速球\NGood thing for you he didn't throw the fastball.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.43,1:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,2,,好在他没投快速球
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.60,1:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,2,,那就让我见识一下快速球\NLet's see that fastball.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.86,1:19:00.52,Default,,0,0,2,,快点\NLet's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.19,1:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,2,,耶！      好球\N- Yeah! - Ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.32,1:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,2,,喂，裁判，别欺人太甚\NHey, ump! Come on. Give us a break!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.07,1:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,2,,裁判\NHey, ump.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.28,1:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,2,,给个警告嘛！      好呀\NHow about a warning? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.12,1:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,2,,小心被球打死\NWatch out you don't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.33,1:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,2,,暂停\NTime!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.50,1:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,2,,暂停\NTime!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.46,1:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,2,,好，前面两球高而且直\NThose first two were high and tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.84,1:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,2,,你想下面一球会如何？\NWhat will the next one be?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.30,1:19:28.36,Default,,0,0,2,,我想…\NWell, either low and away or in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.36,1:19:30.01,Default,,0,0,2,,不是低而外弯就是朝我耳朵来\N我想…\NWell, either low and away or in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.01,1:19:30.09,Default,,0,0,2,,不是低而外弯就是朝我耳朵来
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.09,1:19:31.19,Default,,0,0,2,,他绝不想满垒，所以小心低球\NHe won't want to load the bases. So look for low and away.\N不是低而外弯就是朝我耳朵来
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.19,1:19:33.89,Default,,0,0,2,,他绝不想满垒，所以小心低球\NHe won't want to load the bases. So look for low and away.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.97,1:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,2,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.31,1:19:38.52,Default,,0,0,2,,但是也要注意你的耳朵\NBut watch out for in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.15,1:19:41.44,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉加油      继续打球了\N- Come on, Archie! - Let's go, kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.52,1:19:43.36,Default,,0,0,2,,你一定打得到 葛汉，要有信心\NBatter, batter, batter, batter!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.44,1:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,2,,Come on, Arch. It just takes one.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.57,1:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,2,,这次一定行\NNever hit it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.88,1:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,2,,你永远打不到\N这次一定行\NNever hit it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.24,1:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,2,,你永远打不到
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.33,1:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,2,,让咱们来个满垒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.21,1:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,2,,耶！\NYeah. Yeah.\N让咱们来个满垒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.42,1:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,2,,耶！\NYeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.62,1:20:01.38,Default,,0,0,2,,够远了      回本垒吧\NThat's deep enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.46,1:20:02.71,Default,,0,0,2,,快！快回本垒\NGo! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.04,1:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,2,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.05,1:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,2,,安全上垒      他妈…\NSafe!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.34,1:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,2,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.63,1:20:11.51,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉，打得好\NWay to go, Arch! Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.59,1:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,2,,葛汉，好样子\NAttaboy, Arch!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.68,1:20:16.22,Default,,0,0,2,,为葛汉来个波浪欢呼 好本领\NThis is the wave!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.89,1:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,2,,- Way to go, man! - Yeah, Archie.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.48,1:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,2,,耶，葛汉   你真行\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.73,1:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,2,,我们就需要这一棒 记你一大功\NThat's what we needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.23,1:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,2,,Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.65,1:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,2,,Yeah. Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.56,1:21:02.19,Default,,0,0,2,,这是什么？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.27,1:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,2,,这个混蛋在搞什么？ 嗨！\NWhat is this jerk doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.77,1:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.19,1:21:06.19,Default,,0,0,2,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.27,1:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,2,,要命！      让我来揍他\NWreck him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.44,1:21:08.44,Default,,0,0,2,,Let me at him!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.53,1:21:11.03,Default,,0,0,2,,马克，你打断比赛了\NYou're interrupting the game, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.78,1:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你最好别再做梦\NRay, it's time to put away your little fantasies
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.12,1:21:16.37,Default,,0,0,2,,and come down to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.45,1:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,2,,不是梦，是真的\NIt's not a fantasy. They're real.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.79,1:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,2,,你说谁是真的？\NWho is real?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.75,1:21:24.13,Default,,0,0,2,,赤脚乔和所有的白袜队\NShoeless Joe Jackson, the White Sox, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.21,1:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,2,,你是说…\NYou mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.46,1:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,2,,他看不到\NHe can't see any of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.21,1:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,2,,这又是谁，猫王吗？\NWell, who is this, Elvis?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.30,1:21:32.47,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞\NRay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.30,1:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,2,,告诉你这位是泰伦斯孟\NAs a matter of fact, it's Terence Mann.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.64,1:21:37.93,Default,,0,0,2,,又在胡说了，你好 我是复活节兔子\NHow do you do? I'm the Easter bunny.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.01,1:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，我们要快把事情解决\NLet's settle this thing now. You have no money.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.85,1:21:43.48,Default,,0,0,2,,你没有钱      我绝不卖我的家\NLook. I'm not selling. You have no money!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.81,1:21:48.07,Default,,0,0,2,,你没钱，却有一堆帐单等着付\NYou have a stack of bills! Come fall, you got no crop to sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.15,1:21:49.48,Default,,0,0,2,,到了秋天又没有庄稼能卖钱\NI have a deal that allows you to stay on the land.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.48,1:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,2,,不过我替你想出办法来 让你能继续住下去\N到了秋天又没有庄稼能卖钱\NI have a deal that allows you to stay on the land.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.69,1:21:51.78,Default,,0,0,2,,不过我替你想出办法来 让你能继续住下去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.78,1:21:52.94,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，我们不用卖农场\NWe don't have to sell the farm.\N不过我替你想出办法来 让你能继续住下去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.94,1:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，我们不用卖农场\NWe don't have to sell the farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.28,1:21:58.41,Default,,0,0,2,,把农场卖给我们 房子我们不碰\NYou'll live in the house rent-free.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.49,1:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,2,,你可以免费住在那里 那棒球场怎么办？\NWhat about the team?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.95,1:22:01.62,Default,,0,0,2,,你知道这块土地值多少钱吗？\NDo you realize how much this land is worth?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.70,1:22:03.83,Default,,0,0,2,,知道\NYeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.33,1:22:07.13,Default,,0,0,2,,一亩2，200美金\N2,200 bucks an acre.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.21,1:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,2,,We can't keep a useless baseball diamond in rich farmland.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.77,1:22:11.51,Default,,0,0,2,,那你应该知道 在沃田当中不可能保有棒球场\NWe can't keep a useless baseball diamond in rich farmland.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.51,1:22:11.59,Default,,0,0,2,,那你应该知道 在沃田当中不可能保有棒球场
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.59,1:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,2,,你听好，我们不卖\NRead my lips. We're staying, all right? We're staying.\N那你应该知道 在沃田当中不可能保有棒球场
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.64,1:22:14.55,Default,,0,0,2,,你听好，我们不卖\NRead my lips. We're staying, all right? We're staying.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.63,1:22:16.55,Default,,0,0,2,,可是你就要破产了\NRay, you're bankrupt!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.64,1:22:19.35,Default,,0,0,2,,因为我爱我妹妹 所以才让你保有房子\NI'm offering you a way to keep your home because I love my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.43,1:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,2,,我的合伙人才不管 他已经准备来拍卖了\NMy partners don't care and are ready to foreclose.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.02,1:22:27.06,Default,,0,0,2,,爹地，我们不必卖农场\NDaddy, we don't have to sell the farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.15,1:22:28.56,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦，别闹\NKarin, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.65,1:22:29.98,Default,,0,0,2,,Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.53,1:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,2,,等等，让她说\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.57,1:22:35.20,Default,,0,0,2,,人们会来的\NPeople will come.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.74,1:22:38.62,Default,,0,0,2,,宝贝，什么人？\NWhat people, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.70,1:22:40.20,Default,,0,0,2,,全世界的人\NFrom all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.28,1:22:43.20,Default,,0,0,2,,当他们要渡假时\NThey'll just decide to take a vacation, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.29,1:22:45.41,Default,,0,0,2,,就会来到爱荷华市\NAnd they'll come to Iowa City.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.83,1:22:50.13,Default,,0,0,2,,可是那里很无聊 就会开车来这里付我们钱\NThey'll think it's really boring. So they'll want to pay us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.21,1:22:52.05,Default,,0,0,2,,就像买门票一样\NLike buying a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.22,1:22:58.09,Default,,0,0,2,,你不可能认真吧？\NYou're not seriously listening to this, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.18,1:22:59.22,Default,,0,0,2,,我是认真的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.14,1:23:01.56,Default,,0,0,2,,那你说…\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.72,1:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,2,,人们为什么愿意付钱来这里？\NWhy would anybody pay money to come here?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.77,1:23:06.52,Default,,0,0,2,,看比赛呀\NTo watch the games.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.81,1:23:11.11,Default,,0,0,2,,就像又回到很久很久以前\NIt will be just like when they were little kids a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.19,1:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,2,,他们还是小孩的时候\NThey'll watch the game and remember what it was like.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.61,1:23:14.82,Default,,0,0,2,,看着比赛回忆以前的事\N他们还是小孩的时候\NThey'll watch the game and remember what it was like.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.82,1:23:14.90,Default,,0,0,2,,看着比赛回忆以前的事
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.90,1:23:15.67,Default,,0,0,2,,她到底在说什么？\NWhat the hell is she talking about?\N看着比赛回忆以前的事
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.67,1:23:17.32,Default,,0,0,2,,她到底在说什么？\NWhat the hell is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.41,1:23:18.74,Default,,0,0,2,,人们会来的\NPeople will come.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.82,1:23:21.58,Default,,0,0,2,,All right. This is fascinating,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.66,1:23:25.08,Default,,0,0,2,,好啦，已经够怪异了\Nbut you don't have the money to bring the mortgage up to date.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.16,1:23:26.36,Default,,0,0,2,,问题是你没法准时付贷款\NYou're still going to have to sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.36,1:23:27.62,Default,,0,0,2,,到头来仍要卖掉农场\N问题是你没法准时付贷款\NYou're still going to have to sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.62,1:23:28.67,Default,,0,0,2,,到头来仍要卖掉农场
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.67,1:23:28.73,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你没有选择的余地\NI'm sorry, Ray.\N到头来仍要卖掉农场
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.73,1:23:30.25,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你没有选择的余地\NI'm sorry, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.71,1:23:32.30,Default,,0,0,2,,We got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.30,1:23:36.42,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，人们会来的\NRay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.05,1:23:39.09,Default,,0,0,2,,People will come, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.39,1:23:45.31,Default,,0,0,2,,他们莫名其妙的来到爱荷华\NThey'll come to Iowa for reasons they can't even fathom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.56,1:23:49.77,Default,,0,0,2,,莫名其妙的 把车停在你的车道上\NThey'll turn up your driveway, not knowing for sure why they're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.94,1:23:51.36,Default,,0,0,2,,像天真孩子般的来到你的门口\NThey'll arrive at your door
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.44,1:23:55.11,Default,,0,0,2,,as innocent as children, longing for the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.94,1:23:57.26,Default,,0,0,2,,渴望去寻觅他们的过去\N"Of course, we won't mind if you look around," you'll say.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.26,1:24:00.16,Default,,0,0,2,,你会说 “欢迎你们到处看看”\N渴望去寻觅他们的过去\N"Of course, we won't mind if you look around," you'll say.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.16,1:24:00.62,Default,,0,0,2,,你会说 “欢迎你们到处看看”
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.62,1:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,2,,“一个人只要二十元”\N"It's only $20 per person."\N你会说 “欢迎你们到处看看”
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.83,1:24:02.74,Default,,0,0,2,,“一个人只要二十元”\N"It's only $20 per person."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.12,1:24:06.29,Default,,0,0,2,,他们毫不犹豫的把钱交出来\NThey'll pass over the money without even thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.37,1:24:09.67,Default,,0,0,2,,因为他们愿意 用钱买回那寻觅已久的宁静\NFor it is money they have and peace they lack.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.75,1:24:12.67,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你签字吧\NJust sign the papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.75,1:24:15.34,Default,,0,0,2,,然后在一个晴朗的午后\NThen they'll walk out to the bleachers
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.80,1:24:20.01,Default,,0,0,2,,他们会卷起袖子\Nand sit in their shirt sleeves on a perfect afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.72,1:24:25.89,Default,,0,0,2,,来到垒边的看台上\NThey'll find they have reserved seats
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.97,1:24:28.64,Default,,0,0,2,,在那里会找到 特地为他们预留的座位\Nsomewhere along one of the baselines,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.19,1:24:31.48,Default,,0,0,2,,那正是他们小时候\Nwhere they sat when they were children
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.56,1:24:33.61,Default,,0,0,2,,为英雄们欢呼时所坐过的位子\Nand cheered their heroes,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.19,1:24:36.36,Default,,0,0,2,,他们看着比赛\Nand they'll watch the game,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.44,1:24:40.20,Default,,0,0,2,,就像仙棒一挥 又重回到往日的时光\Nand it will be as if they dipped themselves in magic waters.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.82,1:24:43.16,Default,,0,0,2,,回忆是那么的浓\NThe memories will be so thick,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.24,1:24:46.29,Default,,0,0,2,,化不开也拂不去\Nthey'll have to brush them away from their faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.37,1:24:48.35,Default,,0,0,2,,Ray, when the bank opens in the morning, they'll foreclose.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.35,1:24:50.58,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，明早银行一开门 就会拍卖这个农场\NRay, when the bank opens in the morning, they'll foreclose.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.58,1:24:50.67,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，明早银行一开门 就会拍卖这个农场
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.67,1:24:51.54,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，人们会来的\NPeople will come, Ray.\N瑞，明早银行一开门 就会拍卖这个农场
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.54,1:24:52.50,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，人们会来的\NPeople will come, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.58,1:24:56.13,Default,,0,0,2,,你已经破产了 如果不卖，连房子也保不住\NYou're broke, Ray. You sell now, or you lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.30,1:25:01.63,Default,,0,0,2,,多年来唯一不变的\NThe one constant through all the years, Ray, has been baseball.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.34,1:25:03.63,Default,,0,0,2,,就是棒球\NAmerica has rolled by like an army of steamrollers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.63,1:25:05.55,Default,,0,0,2,,美国的历史、文化 像被蒸汽压路机般辗了又辗\N就是棒球\NAmerica has rolled by like an army of steamrollers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.55,1:25:06.10,Default,,0,0,2,,美国的历史、文化 像被蒸汽压路机般辗了又辗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.10,1:25:07.23,Default,,0,0,2,,更像黑板上的字\NIt's been erased like a blackboard, rebuilt, and erased again.\N美国的历史、文化 像被蒸汽压路机般辗了又辗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.23,1:25:09.30,Default,,0,0,2,,更像黑板上的字\NIt's been erased like a blackboard, rebuilt, and erased again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.30,1:25:10.02,Default,,0,0,2,,擦了写、写了擦\N更像黑板上的字\NIt's been erased like a blackboard, rebuilt, and erased again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.02,1:25:11.24,Default,,0,0,2,,擦了写、写了擦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.44,1:25:14.78,Default,,0,0,2,,但是棒球…\NBut baseball has marked the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.78,1:25:14.81,Default,,0,0,2,,却留下了不朽的脚印\N但是棒球…\NBut baseball has marked the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.81,1:25:16.40,Default,,0,0,2,,却留下了不朽的脚印
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.40,1:25:16.71,Default,,0,0,2,,这个球场、这个比赛\NThis field, this game.\N却留下了不朽的脚印
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.71,1:25:18.90,Default,,0,0,2,,这个球场、这个比赛\NThis field, this game.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.82,1:25:22.03,Default,,0,0,2,,全是我们的过去\NIt's a part of our past, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.86,1:25:25.99,Default,,0,0,2,,它唤起了过去的好时光\NIt reminds us of all that once was good,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.33,1:25:29.16,Default,,0,0,2,,和对将来的憧憬\Nand it could be again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.37,1:25:34.00,Default,,0,0,2,,People will come, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.38,1:25:36.70,Default,,0,0,2,,人们会来\NPeople will most definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.70,1:25:37.80,Default,,0,0,2,,一定会来的\N人们会来\NPeople will most definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.80,1:25:38.75,Default,,0,0,2,,一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.75,1:25:38.93,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你会失去一切\NRay, you will lose everything.\N一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.93,1:25:42.01,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你会失去一切\NRay, you will lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.30,1:25:44.18,Default,,0,0,2,,会被赶出去\NYou will be evicted.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.23,1:25:56.90,Default,,0,0,2,,签吧\NCome on, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.92,1:26:19.46,Default,,0,0,2,,我不签      你疯了\NI'm not signing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.55,1:26:21.88,Default,,0,0,2,,You're crazy. Absolutely nuts!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.47,1:26:23.67,Default,,0,0,2,,你是彻底的疯了\NI can't do it, pal.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.76,1:26:27.55,Default,,0,0,2,,老兄，我不能签\NI mean, you build a baseball field
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.64,1:26:30.72,Default,,0,0,2,,你在这鸟不拉屎的地方 盖了座球场\Nin the middle of nowhere, and you stare at nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.81,1:26:31.77,Default,,0,0,2,,然后盯着空球场猛看\NIt's not nothing. Your daughter's turned into a space case.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.77,1:26:33.06,Default,,0,0,2,,它不是空的\N然后盯着空球场猛看\NIt's not nothing. Your daughter's turned into a space case.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.06,1:26:33.77,Default,,0,0,2,,然后盯着空球场猛看\NIt's not nothing. Your daughter's turned into a space case.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.85,1:26:35.17,Default,,0,0,2,,你把女儿也弄得精神恍惚\NGet your hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.17,1:26:35.73,Default,,0,0,2,,放开她！      我只是想帮你\N你把女儿也弄得精神恍惚\NGet your hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.73,1:26:36.57,Default,,0,0,2,,放开她！      我只是想帮你
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.31,1:26:38.44,Default,,0,0,2,,Karin?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.08,1:26:39.87,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.90,1:26:46.36,Default,,0,0,2,,她还好吗？      我不知道\NIs she all right? Is she breathing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.45,1:26:48.28,Default,,0,0,2,,有呼吸吗？      我去开车\NShould I get the car?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.45,1:26:55.58,Default,,0,0,2,,我去叫救护车\NI'm going to call Emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.87,1:26:58.29,Default,,0,0,2,,安妮，等等\NAnnie, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.88,1:26:59.96,Default,,0,0,2,,你说什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.35,1:27:18.65,Default,,0,0,2,,你等一下\NJust wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.16,1:27:38.71,Default,,0,0,2,,小家伙怎么了？   她摔下来\NWhat have we got here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.79,1:27:40.17,Default,,0,0,2,,She fell.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.76,1:27:50.18,Default,,0,0,2,,她噎住了，把她扶起来\NThis child's choking to death. Get her up.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.10,1:27:52.85,Default,,0,0,2,,扶稳\NHold her steady now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.98,1:28:01.19,Default,,0,0,2,,热狗卡在喉咙里\NHot dog. Stuck in her throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.23,1:28:03.77,Default,,0,0,2,,没事了，过几天又活蹦乱跳啦\NShe'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.86,1:28:07.03,Default,,0,0,2,,She'll be turning handsprings before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.20,1:28:12.70,Default,,0,0,2,,医生，谢谢你\NThank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.08,1:28:15.33,Default,,0,0,2,,不，孩子，谢谢你\NNo, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.95,1:28:17.25,Default,,0,0,2,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.12,1:28:22.54,Default,,0,0,2,,糟糕，你不能再回去了\NOh, my God. You can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.63,1:28:24.30,Default,,0,0,2,,你是不是不能回去了？ 没关系\NHey, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.38,1:28:26.51,Default,,0,0,2,,对不起      真的没关系\NI'm sorry. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.34,1:28:33.35,Default,,0,0,2,,我最好快点回家\NI best be getting on home
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.80,1:28:36.89,Default,,0,0,2,,否则爱丽莎 以为我交女朋友去了\Nbefore Alicia begins to think I got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.31,1:28:43.56,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，医生\NHey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.23,1:28:45.73,Default,,0,0,2,,医生，你医术高明\NGood work, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.74,1:28:49.28,Default,,0,0,2,,你真行\NNice going, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.32,1:28:54.20,Default,,0,0,2,,我们会想你的\NGoing to miss you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.33,1:28:58.83,Default,,0,0,2,,替我赢一场比赛好吗？\NWin one for me one day, will you, boys?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.91,1:29:00.25,Default,,0,0,2,,Okay, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.33,1:29:01.42,Default,,0,0,2,,没问题      我们答应你\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.67,1:29:11.22,Default,,0,0,2,,这些球员是什么时候来的\NWhen did these ballplayers get here?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.93,1:29:18.35,Default,,0,0,2,,喂，菜鸟\NHey, rookie!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.11,1:29:31.61,Default,,0,0,2,,你真的很不错\NYou were good.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.79,1:29:49.76,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，千万不要卖这个农场\NDo not sell this farm, Ray. You got to keep this farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.84,1:29:51.23,Default,,0,0,2,,一定要保住它\NYou've had a rough day. Go inside and get something cold to drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.23,1:29:53.16,Default,,0,0,2,,你今天经历了不少事\N一定要保住它\NYou've had a rough day. Go inside and get something cold to drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.16,1:29:54.18,Default,,0,0,2,,一定要保住它\NYou've had a rough day. Go inside and get something cold to drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.26,1:29:55.53,Default,,0,0,2,,到屋里去喝点冷饮吧\NYeah. That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.53,1:29:56.80,Default,,0,0,2,,好主意\N到屋里去喝点冷饮吧\NYeah. That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.80,1:29:58.19,Default,,0,0,2,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.26,1:30:00.18,Default,,0,0,2,,你千万别卖掉农场\NDon't sell the farm, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.32,1:30:10.40,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞\NRay?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.53,1:30:13.57,Default,,0,0,2,,我们要休息了，明天见\NWe're going to call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.65,1:30:15.24,Default,,0,0,2,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.32,1:30:16.45,Default,,0,0,2,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.06,1:30:18.78,Default,,0,0,2,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.83,1:30:23.21,Default,,0,0,2,,要不要和我们一起去？\NHey, do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.08,1:30:28.50,Default,,0,0,2,,当真？      不是你\NYou mean it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.75,1:30:30.17,Default,,0,0,2,,No, not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.30,1:30:32.38,Default,,0,0,2,,是他\NHim.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.93,1:30:37.97,Default,,0,0,2,,他？\NHim? Come with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.05,1:30:39.14,Default,,0,0,2,,和你一起去？      到那边去\NOut there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.22,1:30:40.47,Default,,0,0,2,,那边有什么？ 你自己去发掘呀\NWhat is out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.56,1:30:41.93,Default,,0,0,2,,Come and find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.02,1:30:43.73,Default,,0,0,2,,等等，球场是我盖的 为什么让他去\NWait a second. Why him?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.81,1:30:46.15,Default,,0,0,2,,I built this field. You wouldn't be here if it weren't for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.23,1:30:48.11,Default,,0,0,2,,如果不是我，你不可能在这里\NRay, I'm unattached. You have a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.19,1:30:49.99,Default,,0,0,2,,你还有家庭呀 我知道\NI want to know what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.99,1:30:51.44,Default,,0,0,2,,可是我也想知道那边有什么\N你还有家庭呀 我知道\NI want to know what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.44,1:30:52.07,Default,,0,0,2,,可是我也想知道那边有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.07,1:30:52.79,Default,,0,0,2,,但是你没有被邀请呀\NBut you're not invited.\N可是我也想知道那边有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.79,1:30:53.99,Default,,0,0,2,,但是你没有被邀请呀\NBut you're not invited.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.90,1:30:58.91,Default,,0,0,2,,没被邀请？这是什么意思？\NNot invited? What do you mean I'm not invited?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.99,1:31:02.24,Default,,0,0,2,,那是我的玉米田 你们都是我的客人\NThat's my corn out there. You guys are guests in my corn.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.33,1:31:04.33,Default,,0,0,2,,我已经奉献得够多了\NI've done everything I've been asked to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.41,1:31:06.67,Default,,0,0,2,,虽然许多吩咐我不明白 但仍照着去做\NI didn't understand it, but I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.75,1:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,2,,从没问过我能得什么好处\NI haven't once asked what's in it for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.75,1:31:09.88,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，你想说什么？ 我想问“我能得到什么好处”\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.96,1:31:12.42,Default,,0,0,2,,I'm saying, "What's in it for me?"
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.67,1:31:15.76,Default,,0,0,2,,难道你做这些全是为了自己\NIs that why you did this?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.84,1:31:17.05,Default,,0,0,2,,For you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.06,1:31:24.60,Default,,0,0,2,,你最好留在这里\NI think you'd better stay here, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.10,1:31:29.19,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.07,1:31:34.03,Default,,0,0,2,,他们选我是有原因的\NThere's a reason they chose me,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.11,1:31:36.57,Default,,0,0,2,,就像他们选中这个球场一样\Njust as there's a reason they chose this field.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.16,1:31:39.91,Default,,0,0,2,,为什么？      因为我是去采访\NI gave that interview.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.99,1:31:41.99,Default,,0,0,2,,采访？你在说什么\NWhat interview? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.08,1:31:45.95,Default,,0,0,2,,我在说那座让你到 波士顿找我的艾柏特球场\NThe one about Ebbets Field, the one that sent you to Boston to find me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.25,1:31:50.79,Default,,0,0,2,,你居然骗我\NYou lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.92,1:31:53.88,Default,,0,0,2,,别忘了你想绑架我\NYou were kidnapping me at the time. You lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.96,1:31:56.26,Default,,0,0,2,,你居然骗我 你还说你有枪\NYou said your finger was a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.59,1:32:00.34,Default,,0,0,2,,这倒没错\NThat's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.43,1:32:01.47,Default,,0,0,2,,Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.01,1:32:05.10,Default,,0,0,2,,Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.68,1:32:09.02,Default,,0,0,2,,你听我说\NListen to me, Ray. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.81,1:32:12.98,Default,,0,0,2,,那边有着不可思议的事\NThere is something out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.69,1:32:16.57,Default,,0,0,2,,如果我能有勇气去探讨\Nand if I have the courage to go through with this,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.65,1:32:18.61,Default,,0,0,2,,那将是个了不起的故事\Nwhat a story it'll make.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.53,1:32:23.37,Default,,0,0,2,,“赤脚乔杰克森来到爱荷华”\N"Shoeless Joe Jackson comes to Iowa."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.29,1:32:33.96,Default,,0,0,2,,你真要写这些故事？\NWhat? Are you going to write about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.04,1:32:35.84,Default,,0,0,2,,那当然\NYou bet I'll write about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.26,1:32:38.51,Default,,0,0,2,,你确实会写这些故事\NYou're going to write about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.01,1:32:40.63,Default,,0,0,2,,这是我的职业呀\NThat's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.81,1:32:45.89,Default,,0,0,2,,好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.31,1:32:50.39,Default,,0,0,2,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.65,1:33:01.82,Default,,0,0,2,,老公？\NHoney?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.16,1:33:08.16,Default,,0,0,2,,老公，他到哪去？\NHoney, where's he going?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.91,1:33:11.50,Default,,0,0,2,,他们邀泰瑞到那边去\NTerry's been invited to go out with the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.58,1:33:13.42,Default,,0,0,2,,你觉得怎样？ 很蠢\NHow are you feeling, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.50,1:33:14.63,Default,,0,0,2,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.88,1:33:16.09,Default,,0,0,2,,那边？      对\NYou mean out?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.17,1:33:17.46,Default,,0,0,2,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.46,1:33:19.51,Default,,0,0,2,,未知的那边\NOut.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.34,1:33:21.55,Default,,0,0,2,,哇，好棒\NFar out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.80,1:33:25.80,Default,,0,0,2,,我要全部细节\NI want a full description.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.35,1:33:28.35,Default,,0,0,2,,好好照顾这个家\NTake care of this family.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.89,1:33:32.27,Default,,0,0,2,,你要多加小心\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.45,1:34:32.54,Default,,0,0,2,,再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.79,1:34:36.92,Default,,0,0,2,,怎么啦？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.13,1:34:46.68,Default,,0,0,2,,你这个幽灵在笑什么？\NWhat are you grinning at, you ghost?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.05,1:34:48.68,Default,,0,0,2,,“如果你盖了…”\N"If you build it,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.10,1:34:52.60,Default,,0,0,2,,“他就会来”\N"he will come."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.65,1:35:06.03,Default,,0,0,2,,喔，我的天\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.78,1:35:08.41,Default,,0,0,2,,什么事？到底怎么了\NWhat? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.33,1:35:13.87,Default,,0,0,2,,那是我父亲\NIt's my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.21,1:35:20.79,Default,,0,0,2,,“抚平他的伤痛”\N"Ease his pain."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.13,1:35:23.80,Default,,0,0,2,,“到远方去”\N"Go the distance."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.97,1:35:28.34,Default,,0,0,2,,原来是你\NIt was you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.39,1:35:33.64,Default,,0,0,2,,不，瑞，是你自己\NNo, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.14,1:35:35.48,Default,,0,0,2,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.00,1:36:03.38,Default,,0,0,2,,天呀\NMy God. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.63,1:36:08.22,Default,,0,0,2,,我只看到 几年后他被岁月折磨后的老态\NI only saw him years later when he was worn down by life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.14,1:36:11.51,Default,,0,0,2,,看看他现在…\NLook at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.39,1:36:17.56,Default,,0,0,2,,这么年轻而且意气风发 眼里闪烁着青春的光芒\NHe's got his whole life in front of him, and I'm not even a glint in his eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.77,1:36:24.57,Default,,0,0,2,,我该怎么和他说呢？\NWhat do I say to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.65,1:36:29.70,Default,,0,0,2,,你可以 先介绍他认识自己的孙女\NWhy don't you introduce him to his granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.99,1:36:34.03,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.41,1:36:36.45,Default,,0,0,2,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.04,1:36:40.29,Default,,0,0,2,,首先要谢谢你们盖这座球场\NI just wanted to thank you folks for putting up this field,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.37,1:36:42.13,Default,,0,0,2,,让我们能来这里打球\Nletting us play here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.83,1:36:44.50,Default,,0,0,2,,我叫约翰康斯拉\NI'm John Kinsella.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.63,1:36:47.88,Default,,0,0,2,,我是瑞\NI'm Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.42,1:36:52.09,Default,,0,0,2,,这是我太太安妮\NMy wife Annie. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.18,1:36:53.97,Default,,0,0,2,,这是我女儿凯伦\NThis is my daughter Karin.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.05,1:36:55.85,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦，这是我父…\NKarin, this is my...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.77,1:37:00.23,Default,,0,0,2,,这是约翰\NThis is John.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.35,1:37:02.60,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，约翰\NHi, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.07,1:37:06.44,Default,,0,0,2,,凯伦，你好\NHiya, Karin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.07,1:37:11.74,Default,,0,0,2,,我们让你们俩去聊聊\NWell, we're going to let you two talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.41,1:37:15.16,Default,,0,0,2,,如果真有那么多人要来 那可有得忙了\NI mean, if all these people are going to come,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.24,1:37:17.24,Default,,0,0,2,,we got a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.58,1:37:21.75,Default,,0,0,2,,非常高兴见到你\NIt was very nice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.92,1:37:24.08,Default,,0,0,2,,是我的荣幸\NMa'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.42,1:37:26.88,Default,,0,0,2,,宝贝，我们走吧\NCome on, hon.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.60,1:37:43.48,Default,,0,0,2,,你是个好捕手\NYou catch a good game.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.77,1:37:46.11,Default,,0,0,2,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.44,1:37:50.32,Default,,0,0,2,,这里真美\NIt's so beautiful here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.49,1:37:53.78,Default,,0,0,2,,对我来讲…\NFor me...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.07,1:37:58.87,Default,,0,0,2,,就像是梦幻成真一样\NWell, for me it's like a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.66,1:38:04.62,Default,,0,0,2,,我能问你一件事吗？\NCan I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.34,1:38:10.30,Default,,0,0,2,,这里是不是天堂？\NIs... Is this heaven?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.59,1:38:15.93,Default,,0,0,2,,这是爱荷华\NIt's Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.93,1:38:19.01,Default,,0,0,2,,爱荷华？\NIowa?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.81,1:38:20.93,Default,,0,0,2,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.14,1:38:26.56,Default,,0,0,2,,我发誓这里真像天堂\NI could have sworn it was heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.91,1:38:35.99,Default,,0,0,2,,Is...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.99,1:38:38.66,Default,,0,0,2,,难道真有天堂吗？\NIs there a heaven?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.83,1:38:42.12,Default,,0,0,2,,有的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.04,1:38:46.37,Default,,0,0,2,,就是让梦幻成真的地方\NIt's the place dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.48,1:39:08.27,Default,,0,0,2,,那么这里或许真是天堂\NMaybe this is heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.28,1:39:14.49,Default,,0,0,2,,好吧…\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.20,1:39:16.82,Default,,0,0,2,,瑞，晚安\NGood night, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.28,1:39:20.91,Default,,0,0,2,,晚安，约翰\NGood night, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.17,1:39:33.09,Default,,0,0,2,,嗨，爸爸？\NHey, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.88,1:39:38.89,Default,,0,0,2,,我们来玩接球，好吗？\NYou want to have a catch?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.39,1:39:42.89,Default,,0,0,2,,当然好\NI'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.74,1:41:29.07,Default,,0,0,2,,剧终
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.14,1:45:27.20,Default,,0,0,2,,献给天下的父母们
